verse:
. OBI wɔ hɔ a ɔkyɛn obiara, 
Ɔsɛ dɛ yɛfrɛ N'nyɛnko;
No dɔ kyɛn onua mpo no dɔ, 
Aboɔdzen, wɔnntɔ, onnyi ewiei;
Hɔn a wɔsɔ No dɔ n' hwɛ n', 
Hu dɛ ɔyɛ onnyiewiei dɔ.

. Nyɛnko bɛn na ɔbɛgye hɛn a, 
Nkyɛ obotum ehue no bɔgyaa n'?
Naaso hɛn Jesus wui gyee hɛn; 
Ɔkaa hɛn nye Nyame bɔɔ m';
Iyi, dɔ a onnyi mbanano a;
Jesus yɛ nyɛnko mapa.

. Ber a ɔbaa adasa wiadze no,
Ne dzin nye Abɔn Damfoedu;
Afei ɔwɔ N'enyimnyam mu,
Odzi dɛw wɔ dzin yi mu;
Ɔfrɛ hɛn 'nuamom, ndamfo,
Na ɔhwɛ hɛn ehiadze nyina.

. Kobɔfo, ka w' ho, mma nnkyim;
Mbeamùdua n' ho wɔ kwan!
Hwehwɛ beà a woehyira do n':
Mbeamùdua n' ho wɔ kwan!
'Wo a wo kɔn ebu, aberɛ,
Jesus tum deda adwen;
Jesus tum deda adwen;
Hom wɔ w'Agyenkwa no mu:
Mbeamùdua n' ho wɔ nkwan!

Nyew, yebehyia baka no ho,
Baka fɛɛfɛw, baka fɛɛfɛw no ho;
Yɛnyѐ esiarfo n' behyia baka no ho;
Ofi Nyame N'eguam' pem n'.

. Dwen prɛko bio dɛ ɔwɔ ha ndɛ;
Bu Ne siar frɛ no bi, na dzi do;
Tsie, N'awɔse ndze n'rowosow dɛ:
Ao, me mba, ao, hom mbra!

Suo mu bi, suo mu bi, tsen wo nsa suo mu bi;
   Afonafo retsew hwe; tsen wo nsa suo mu bi;
   Suo mu bi, suo mu bi, tsen wo nsa suo mu bi,
   Jesus da ho refrɛ; tsen wo nsa suo m’ bi.

. Anà ayɛ komm tse hɔ ? Ndwom wɔ ha a wɔtow;
Bohur N’ayɛyi ndwom, bosuo mu ma yɛntow;
Gyedzi ndze nyina sesa, po nye aman do,
Ma ɔkɛpem sor do; tsen wo nsa suo mu bi.

. Woarà ankasa nye kwan n’,
Kyérɛ Woho wɔ mo mu;
Ama maahwer me mher tsiabaa ’i,
Wɔ W'apɛdze ne yɛ m’;
Ama maadɔ m’ Nyame.
Osiandέ odzii kan dɔɔ m';
Na meeyi Wo ayɛw daa wɔ
W‘enyimnyam tsѐnabew hɔ.

. MEYƐ hɔho wɔ ha,
Sor nye me fie;
Asaase yέ awerɛhow,
Sor nye me fie;
Mbusu nye awerɛhow,
Etwa mo ho ehyia;
Ɔsor nye m'Egya kùrowm',
Sor nye me fie.

. Kaansa ehum rutù a,
Sor nye me fie;
M'akwantu ɔyɛ tsia,
Sor nye me fie;
Mber n'ehum nye me fie;
Ɔnnkyɛr na abɔ adze;
Na ewiei n' m'bokodu fie
Sor nye me fie.

. Dɛm ntsi minndzi nkɔmbɔ,
Sor nye me fie;
Me kyɛpɛn tse dɛn ara a,
Sor nye me fie;
Mo Wura abanyimfa
Na m'begyina ampa;
Ɔsor nye m'Egya kùrom',
Sor nye me fie.

NYAME, fa wo nhyira pon hɛn,
Ma yɛnkɔ asomdwee mu;
Yɛnda ho ndzi sor edziban;
Dɔr hɛn gyedzi nye hɛn dɔ:
Fa akomatɔmù hyɛ hɛn mu;
Yɛdze hɛn 'koma ma Wo;
Yenya du hɛn siar bea no dὸ a,
Yɛbɛma Wo ayɛyi pa!
Alleluia.      Amen.

. EWÙRADZE a meda ho twer Wo,
'Besie m' nokwarm' akɔ ewiei;
Wo nokwar, Wo dɔ, nye Wo tum
Bɛgye m' akɔ me mber ewiei;
Sɛ moto honam yi ase a
'Dze kyɛw a ɔnnsɛɛ botua m' kaw.

. Sosὸ a, abɛn kɛse n' ɔmbɔm',
Na hɛn nkorɔfo nsoɛr;
Hom a hom gu daadzetsirm', hom nyan;
'Hotsewfo, hom mfow sor.

. N-kwa da ketseaba yi rotwe kɔ;
Wiadze dɛw repa; n' enyimnyam resen;
N-sakyer na ɔsɛɛ nkὸ ara na muhu;
Ao, 'Wὸ a ennsakyer da, enye me ntsѐna.

. Murumua m' enyi a, yi Wo mbeamùdua n' kyѐrɛ m';
Hyerɛn wɔ sum mu, kyѐrɛ m' ɔsor do kwan;
Ɔsor rehyѐrɛn, wiadze kusuww repa;
N-kwam' o, owum' o, enye me ntsѐna!

. KANEÀ a yɛdze hwɛ hɛn kwan mu,
Mma yaammfom kwan yɛannyew;
Adom n-sù a ofi sor tɔ
Ma akwantufo nom bi;

. WƆMBƆ abɛn n' mu, wɔmbɔm',
Ahomkà awɔsѐ abɛn n';
Wɔmma amanaman ntse,
Nkɛpem wiadze ntuadze;
Afahodzi afe n' aba!
Hom a wɔapon hom, hom nsan mbra.

. Jesus, Sɔfopanyin,
Ɔaba werdam prɛko;
Sunsùm a wɔahaw, wɔnhom;
Awѐrɛfo ndzi dɛw,
Afahodzi afe n' aba!
Hom a wɔapon hom, hom nsan mbra.

. Wo dwuma dzi ma w' Agyenkwa
Na wo nkorafo adasa;
Yɛ ntsɛm, buber n' abɛn ampa;
Fonafo, rotweɔn ayɛ dɛn?

. Asomdwee Hen!
Amanaman ruwu;
Wo mba a apon hɔn rotɔ akono.

. 'Wo a kitsa samanadze saafee
Akra a woenya Wo no wɔnnhwehwɛ hwee;
'Wo yɛ Nokwar, Ɔkwan, N-kwa ma abɔn;
Annkɔa -wɔnnkɔ Christ e, gya m' kodu sɔnn.

. Medan Wo gya a, mabra; adze ehu m';
Motwer Wo a, mewie, owu nnkotum me;
M'adagyaw mu, boa me menyɛ tartweɔn:
Ankor-n'apem-Nyame, gya m' kodu sɔnn,

. Sɛ 'Wo Christ gyà m' a, mowɔ asomdwee;
Me hia mu W'asɛm yɛ m' edzi-amee;
Migyaa moho ma Wo Sunsum Krɔnkrɔn,
Dɛ ekyim o, ntsɛm o, gya m' kodu sɔnn.

. Nyame, ndɔbaa Wura,
Tsie Wo mba mpaayi;
Hɛn nkwa nyina fir Woara;
Gye hɛn ayɛyi.

. Abɔdze biara nya N' akɔndɔdze;
Nam, nnoma na hambowa nyina so;
Ɔkyɛso Nyame ma wonya wodzi,
Ntsi wohuhor Ne dzin afebɔɔ.

. JESUS, 'Hyɛse na Ewiei,
Me kra twer Wo nko ara;
Ɔwo pepaa mo bɔn
Dze hyɛɛ W'edwuma ase;
Ibotu m' bɔn ase
Na esi m' pi wɔ ɔdɔ m'.

. Enyimnyam nkã Egya Nyame
Wɔ No domankoma dɔ;
Wɔmfa Jesus Ne dzin ntahye
Wɔ mbrɛ nyimpa biara wɔ;
Sunsum Krɔnkrɔn n' wɔmma N' nhyira
M-fesantsen mbersantsen;
Na hɛn ndwom dabaa nyinara
Nyɛ dɛ, Jesus bedzi Hen!

. AMAN Wurà a W' adom dɔɔ sõ,
Wo nkὸwaà atɔbɔ tonton Wo dzin;
Ayɛ hɛn man n' Apatasu;
Wo tum nwanwa fir mbersantsen.
Asɛɛ tamfo n' mamman;
Agye hɛn so hɛn man;
Aman-suro Nyame,
'Wo nye mbɔbɔrhunyi.
Yehuhor Wo, Ɔnwanwanyi!

. Adzekyee pa nya kye hɛn a,
Ma yɛnde Wo yie ase;
Boa ma yɛmfa hɛn bra nyina,
Ndzi W' adɔyɛ ho dase;
Mber n' nya ba a, Agyenkwa Christ,
Fa hɛn kodu Paradisѐ.

ADZE kor na minyim dɛ nkyɛ kobɔnyi,
Adze kor, adze kor;
Na ndɛ ɔagye m’ nkwa, Jesus dze m’ asan fie;
Dza minyim nye adze kor.
M’asɛm yi dze m’bɔbɔ n’dawur akyerɛ aman,
Na matow ehùrusi ndwom meyi mo Pomfὸ ayɛw;
Medze moho nyina bɛma N’
Nyew minyim nye adze kor.

. M’EWIEI bowie me dεn ;
Asεm yi som mo bo,
Ɔse dε modwen ho yie,
Wɔ ber yi ara mu,
Ahyεse nnhia dέ ewiei; 
Nokwar yi onnsuma;
Dεm ntsi bεn mowɔ yε ?
M’bεper ahwehwε nkwa.

. Adze asa m’ m’akwantu mu,
Honam tamfo hyɛ m’ amen so;
Ɔwo na mekã m’asɛm kyѐrɛ W’;
Hu ‘wѐrɛhonyi mbɔbɔr.

. Tsie, owu yɛ nda ma kwantunyi;
Ɔbra n’akotorka dzenndzen,
Ɔbra n’enyibɔ nyina twa m’ sen;
Tsie, owu yɛ nda ma kwantunyi.

. Ao, owu yɛ dɛw ma Christ suanyi;
Bɛkyebo dɛw, bɛkyebo nkwa.
Na owu ma yenya no kwa;
Ao, owu yɛ dɛw ma Christ suanyi.

. Wiadze mbusù a ! Mo nkὸrɔfo,
M’enyidar Christ yɛ m’ Nyɛnko;
Dɛm ntsi munnsuro owu;
Nyame, gye me kra.

. Na mo wu m’ meepinkyɛn wo,
Dɛ, munnsuro, munnsuro;
Menye W' nam a, munnsuro.

. Wo nokwar si pi, ɔnnsakyer; 
Nyia ɔfrɛ Wo n' egye no nkwa;
Iye ma nyia ɔhwehwɛ Wo,
Nyia ohu Wo n' N' adze nyina.

. MIHYIRA Nyame N' Christ;
Motwer Nyame dɔ no;
Na medze ano na akoma krɔnn, 
Gye Agyenkwa n' yɛ medze.

. Miyi adom Nyame ayɛw;
Motwer N' nokwar, No tum n';
Meyɛ Nedze, ɔyɛ medze,
Nyame, me dɛw, me kan.

. Mo nkwa hyɛ No mu daa,
Mo wu etwa m' kɔ ampa;
Mo fua nyina anan ayɛ kan;
M'adzesaa adan adzekyee.

. Sɛ adzekyee twe no ho a,
M'adwen nyina nyɛ dɛm;
Ayɛyi nka Jesus! 
Adzesaa dan 'dzekyee, 
Ber a yɛka n' hɛn akoma m';
Ayɛyi nka Jesus!

. Jesus, dzin a ɔtahye! 
Ɔsor nye asaase dɛw; 
Yennya mboa beebiara,
Yennyi dzin biara so a 
Yɛnam do benya hɛn nkwagye; 
Jesus baa wiadze bɛgyee nkwa.

. Jesus, dzin dɛɛdɛw bi! 
Okenyan sor dɔm no;
Wɔpaa m' bɔ Ne dzin no,
No dɔ n' yɛ hɔn nwanwa:
Hɔn enyigye nyina nye dɛ wɔhwɛ N';
Hɛn heaven nye yehu N' enyim.

. Ɔbɔn tse Ne dzin no
Na onya ahotɔ;
Ɔyɛ ndwom wɔ n'asomu,
Ɔyɛ nkwa, konyimdzi;
Ndwom fofor hyɛ ne gyirama ma; 
Onya akoma mu dɛw, ɔsaw.

. M'AKOMA na gyirama,
Mema do wɔ ayɛyi m'; 
Obiara ntonton Messiah;
Amanaman Nyame a
Ɔdze No tum-sɛm no
Bɔɔ wiadze wiee ma odzii mu.

. Wobeyi akra efi bɔn no mpokyerɛ m',
Ekyingye nnkɛyɛ N' asɛm no sunkamm;
Hɛll nnkɛyɛ hu na owu rinnya bɔr; 
Ɔdɔ dzi konyim, ber a Jesus dzi Hen.

. 'Nyansafo, hom mfi hom dadaw m',
Kan fɛɛfɛw bi wɔ ekyir;
Hom nhwehwɛ aman apɛdze,
Hom ehu N'awoo ho woraba;
Hom mbra mbɔsom,
Mbɔsom Christ, Ɔhen a wɔawo N'.

. O Christianfo, hom nnyan na adze akye, 
Anapa yi na wɔwoo Agyenkwa;
Hom nsoɛr na hom ntonton Nyame dɔ,
Esumasɛm a abɔfo tow ho ndwom;
Hɔn na wodzii kan kaa n-sɛmpa no,
Mbrɛ Nyame bɛbrae ma ɔbaabun woo N'.

. Dɛm na hɛn ho bɛtsew ma yaafora 
Abɔfodɔm yɛatow konyimdzi ndwom;
Nyia wɔawo N' n-dɛ enyigye da yi,
Ɔdze enyimnyam bɛhyerɛn hɛn ho nyina;
No dɔ bɛgye hɛn nkwa na yaatow ndwom
Afebɔɔ yɛakamfo sor Hen tumfo n'.

. Adzekyee mba nyinara mu dansewa, 
Pa hɛn isum na fa wo mboa brɛ hɛn;
Boka nworaba a epue ma wim' atsew wann,
Gya hɛn kɔ mbrɛ wɔawo Gyefo ama hɛn.
 
. N' adasoe do na bɔw rososɔ hyɛnhyɛnn; 
Nantwibuwm' na ɔdze Ne tsir ato komm;
Ɔda hɔ n' abɔfo ruhuahua no dɛ,
Adasa Yɛfo, Ɔhen na Gyefo.
 
. Aso ampa dɛ hɛn so yɛbɛkyɛ No 
Edom nduhuam na asomfo akyɛdze,
Mbepɔw do mbobaa, po do nankyenema,
Kwaa mu wandze, daadzetsirmu sika?
 
. Hɛn ayɛyɛdze piigyan nyina nnsɛ hwee; 
Akyɛdze biara nntum nnya N' enyimpa;
Akomam' ndaase na abɔbɔfo mpaabɔ
Som bo kɛsekɛse ma Onyame.
 
. Adekyee mba nyinara mu dansewa, 
Pa hɛn isum na fa wo mboa brɛ hɛn;
Boka nworaba a epue ma wim' atsew wann,
Gya hɛn kɔ mbrɛ wɔawo Gyefo ama hɛn.

. O Bethlehem Ɔba krɔnkrɔn,
Yeserɛ Wo, bra hɛn nkyɛn;
Pam hɛn bɔn na afei tsena hɛn mu;
Ma wɔnwo W' hɛn mu ndɛ.
Yɛtse Borɔnya abɔfo n'
Nka dɛ wɔrobɔ amandzɛɛ n';
O bra hɛn nkyɛn, nye hɛn ntsena,
Hɛn Wura Immuanuel.  Amen

. ƆSORSOR, hom nyi Ewuradze ayɛw; 
Ewia, bosoom, dzi N'enyim dɛw; 
Nworaba, kan, hom ntonton No. 
 
. Yi Ewuradze ayɛw na ɔakasa a, 
Wiadze tsiee ne ndze kɛse n'; 
mbrasɛm a wonnkobu do da, 
Wɔ hɔ ma hɛn akwankyerɛ.

. Yi Ewuradze ayɛw, nyimnyamfo no a;
 N'anohoba nnyɛ gyan da; 
Ɔama N'ahotsewfo konyim; 
Bɔn na wu nnkedzi nyim da. 
 
. Yi hɛn nkwagye Nyame ayɛw; 
Sor dɔm mpaa mu nka No tum; 
Sor na asaase nye abɔdze nyina
Ntonton No, nhuhor Ne dzin.   Amen.

. Wiadze ehu amandze akyɛr 
Wɔ bɔn na aperdzi ho;
Abɔfo ndwom dɛɛdɛw n' ekyir,
Bɔn etsim mfe mpenu;
Adasa roko ntsi wɔnntse
Dɔ ndwom a wɔdze ma, n';
O akofo, hom nyɛ komm ntsie
Sor abɔfo ndwom no.

. Ɔsor man hyɛnhyɛnn no mu
Wonnhia abɔdze kan biara;
Ɔwo nye n' kan, dɛw, abɔtsir,
Ɔwo nye n'ewia a ɔnntɔ da;
Yɛntow W'ayɛyi wɔ hɔ, 
Hallelujah nka hɛn Hen.   Amen.

. Ewuradze, fa Wo kan bra, 
Gyedzi a otu hɛn suro no a;
Ma Wo dɔ nkitsa hɛn 'koma,
Gya hɛn kɔ W' asomdwee kwan mu;
Hɛn akra a wosuro wu dzen,
Gya hɔn twa no sunsuma mu.

. Ma W' adom ne nhyehyɛɛ nda edzi, 
Nyame a ɔbɛyɛɛ nyimpa maa m';
Mo sunsum nyɛ Wo fie krɔnkrɔn,
Yɛ me kan na mo nkwagye mu;
Gya me twa owu sum no mu
Kodu W' ahengua enyim hɔ.

. AWƆW kɛse ber mu,
Mframa nwin bi bɔe;
Famu yɛɛ dɛ dadze,
N-su kyeen dɛ ɔbo;
Esukwankyɛba tɔɔ pii,
'Sukwankyɛba;
Awɔw kɛse ber mu,
Tsetseber mu.

. Hɛn Nyame, sor nntum nnkora W',
Asaase so nntum;
Sor na asaase boguan
Ber a obedzi adze;
Awɔw kɛse ber no mu ',
Mbowadan mpo ye;
Ewuradze Nyame Tumfo,
O Jesus Christ!

. Yɛsom Nyametsir no,
Nyame Dɔ a ɔyɛɛ Nyimpa; 
Yɛsom hɛn Jesus Christ;
Yɛmfa asɛnkyerɛdze bɛn?

. NYAME fi sor atse;
Hom ngyaa nkrumsi nyina;
Na hom nhwɛ, wimu ebue!
'Somdwee akyɛdze n' esian.

. Ɔdɔ a wonntum nnhwehwɛ m' 
Na ɔdze Agyenkwa aba;
Adom no bor nyimpa
Nye abɔfo adwen do;
O Nyame, ma yenhu no dɛ
Hɛn Nyame Noara ɔabɛbra.

. Ɔpeen dɛ ɔba honam m',
Dze sor na ase abɔ m';
'Bɛda hɛn bɔn edzi,
Ma yaayɛ Nyame dze;
Na yaabɔ Nyankopɔm do bra,
'Siandɛ Nyame ada edzi wɔ ha.

. Nwoma Krɔnkrɔn ka dɛ ofi sor
Bɛyɛɛ nyimpa ama oeewu;
Ma wɔdze hɛn bɔn aakyɛ hɛn;
Iyi ntsi na ɔbaa wiadze.

. N'akwan yɛɛ ahobrɛadze;
'No dɔ gyee hɛn ayɛyi,
N'adɔe,, hɛn mpaabɔ;
Tokyemfo nyina betsiee No;
Awerɛhofo twee bɛɛn No 
Benyaa awerɛkyekyer.

. Ber a ɔnam haban mu no, 
Ɔhwɛɛ nhyiren, nnoma na buw, 
Buu Nyame ho mbɛ;
Na No dɔ akoma m' kasa
Kaa nyimpa mba hɔn akra;
Hɔ na Nyame wɔ.

. Yεannhyε nyimpa kakra no nsew,
Hɔn a wohun dε efoow sor n’;
Wɔdze ahobow hwεε sor hann,
Na wobutuuw famù wɔsɔɔr Wo;
Naaso yεgye dzi dε nyimpa
Enyi hun mbrε isii kr sor.

. Awerɛkyekyer nsɛm na ayamuyie 
Dze gyee tsetseber do abɔnfo; 
Hɔn werɛ kyekyee, nyaa dza wohia;
Sa ayarfo yar, bue efurafo enyi.

. Mber a no mu yɛ sum 
Etwa mber pa no ntamu;
M-fe rugu m' n', Wo ndze sesa; 
Yɛnyɛ dɛn ndzi W'ekyir?

. Yɛtse Wo ndze wɔ ekyir, 
Fi Galilee bɔnsa m'; 
Tsetse nwin ka W'edwuma hyɛ; 
Yenyɛ dɛn ndzi W'ekyir.

. Ɔwo etse kan kɛse mu,
Bɔn na 'nyimguase nnyi m';
Dɛ bɔsoa hɛn bɔn, 'nyimguase;
M'bɛyɛ dɛm dɔ n'?

. ƆWO nye mo nkwa; sɛ ekɔ gya me a,
M'abrabɔ 'wu ara nko; Ɔwo nye m' kwan;
Mennya Wo a, m'bɔfom kwan m'akwantu mu.

. Ɔwo nye m' kan; mennya W'enyimnyam kan a,
'Sum kebii bɛma n;enyi ayɛ kusuww;
Me Nyame nye mo kwan, n-kwa, na kan.

. Ɔwo nye m' kwan; ekɔ gya me a, meyew;
Ɔwo nye m' kan; isuma a, munnhu adze!
Ɔwo nye m' nkwa: etwe Woho a, muwu.

. Yi Wo nserɛmɛn kyerɛ m'; enye me ntsena;
Hwɛ, munnhu adze, mewu, m'afom kwan;
Ɔwo nye me kan, mo nkwa na mo kwan!

. Christ, ayɛ abofra pɛn;
Hɛn mbofraber m' Gyafo
Na hɛn kan nye hɛn dɛw;
Na kɔ do nye hɛn ntsena.
Ama Wo dɔ kɛse a wɔnntɔ n'
Aatwe hɛn abɛn Wo daa daa.

. O emi a metse dɛ abofra
Bɛka Wo do a monnkͻhom da;
Kɛpem dɛ dɛw mu ebͻhom
W’ adwen pa no egu mo bo m’;
Anaa dɛ yɛnnkɛpaapaa m’ da,
Dɛ menye Wo yɛ kor sunsum m’!

. Me haw m’ Wo dͻ mma m’ asomdwee,
Me mberɛwyɛ m’ Wo dͻ mma m’ tum;
Ber a ͻbra n’ehum begyaa n’,
Dɛm dͻnhwer soronko no mu,
Wͻ wu m’, dɛ eyɛ nkwa no, gya m’;
Gye me nkwa, Ͻwo a iwui maa m’.  Amen.

. Egya, yɛkamfo Wo dɔ a
Ɔmaa Wo Ba n' bowui;
Adom na nokwar, Jesus,
Wo na yɛntonton Wo;
Sunsum, Ɔwerɛkyekyefo,
Obiara nyi Wo ayɛw;
Nkpem dɛ yɛbɔtow ndwom,
Na asaase adan ɔsor.   Amen.

. JESUS pɛ dɛ abɔnfo wu?
'Bɛn ntsi na ɔsɛɛn dua no do?
No wu ntseam' no ase nye dɛn?
Ɔbɔɔ mpaa maa abɔnfo nyina;
Fa kyɛ hɔn, Egya, fa kyɛ hɔn;
Wonnyim, Me ntsi na wɔtse ase.

. Wodze Guanhwɛfo n' abɔ afɔr ama nguan n'; 
Akowaa ayɛ bɔn, Ba n' agye ho ntsea;
Ber a nyimpa noara no nkwagye nnyɛ n' asɛm,
Nyankopɔn per no.

. W' amandzehu yayaw no, 
Wo bɔgyaa fifir no,
Wo dɔ a ɔmaa iwui ntsi,
Yɛserɛ W' , yi hɛn bɔn kɔ;
Bubu hɛn mpokyerɛ mu na
Gye hɛn emumuyɛ nyinam';
O, yeserɛ W', kaa Calvary,
Na ma yɛnkɔ asomdweem'!
 
. Gyedzi mfa Wo bɔgyaa no 
Nsɔw hɛn bɔfakyɛ ano;
Si n' pi dɛ woebu hɛn bem,
Yɛ hɛn yar nyina edur;
W' amandzehu wɔ dua n' do
Ntsi, twa hɛn yaw nye fona do;
O, yɛserɛ W', kaa Calvary,
Na ma yɛnkɔ asomdweem'!

. HƆN a wotwa mu nyina
Wɔntwe mbɛn Jesus;
Ɔnnyɛ hom asɛm dɛ Jesus wu anaa?
Ɔyɛ hom asomdwee,
Hom kyigyinafo;
Hom mbra mbɔhwɛ dɛ yaw bi nye Nedze n' sɛ a.

. Owu dze pata
Binom hɔn bɔn koraa;
Wo kaw no oetua, na ɔayɛ w'edwuma n'.
Obiara benya
Asomdwee a ogyaae;
Ɔno na ɔserɛɛ dɛ: M'Egya, fa kyɛ hɔn.

. Megye me fakyɛ,
Meyɛ ɔbɔnfo;
Ɔdzebɔnyɛnyi, megye Jesus dzin dzi.
Ɔtɔɔ adom a\nAfei mesuo m' yi;
O Egya, inyim dɛ obowui maa me.

. WƆAKRƆN W' nyimguase dua n' do,
Awerɛhow Hen, menye W' weɔn;
Sum gye W'enyim a atow no do,
Obi nntum nnhu Wo yaw no;
Obi nntum nnkyerɛ amandze a 
Wo nko rosɔw no komm no.

. Ɔdɔ nye awerɛhow bi nnyi
Tse dɛ m'Agyenkwa dze n';
Hwɛ, ɔda mbeamudua no do!
Hɛn adzesoa ahyɛ No do;
Hom nka dɛ N'awoo fi sor!
Hom nhu dɛ ɔyɛ Nyame;
Gyedzi tsea m' dɛ, ɔyɛ Ɔno,
Me Nyame a ohu amandze!

. HOM nkɔ sum Gethsemane, 
Hom a ɔsɔhwɛfo n' haw hom;
Hom nhwɛ hom Gyefo No ko,
Hom nye No nweɔn dɔnhwer kor;
Mma hom nndan mmfi Ne yaw ho;
Hom nhwɛ Jesus nsua mpaabɔ.

. Dzi ekyir kɔ atsɛmbu da n' mu;
Hwɛ Nkwa Wura a wɔakyer no,
O bɔwen na bɔwema!
O ɔhaw a Ne kra hunii a!
Mma nnguan yaw na enyimguase;
Sua No soa mbeamudua no.

. Dzi ekyir kɔ nda n' do ntsɛmara, 
Beebi a wɔdze fun no toe;
Abɔfo tse hɔ roweɔn;
Woana abɛfa No kɔ?
Christ asoɛr! Ɔpɛ akɔ sor;
Gyefo, kyerɛ hɛn ma yɛnsoɛr.

. Ne mbeamudua n' yi hɛn afɔdzi; 
Ɔtaa hɔn a wɔtɔ bitsi;
Ɔhyɛ hɛn dzen mbusu ber mu;
Ɔma dza ɔyɛ wen yɛ dɛw.

. Ewuradze yε Nyame ampa;
Ͻnoara na ᴐyεε hεn;
Yεyε Nedze, ᴐnyεn hεn daa;
N’edzidzibea do nguan nye hεn.

. O hom nhεn N'aponkεse mu;
Hom mbedzi dεw N'abanguado;
Hom nyhira N', nyi Ne dzin ayεw;
Na hεn Nyame fata ndaase:

. Osiandε Ewuradze yε pa;
N'ehumbᴐbᴐr so tsim hᴐ daa;
No nokwardzi si pi ampa,
Na ᴐnnkᴐbᴐ adze ara da.	Amen.

. Minya gyirama wɔ hen 
Dze eyi Wo ayɛw
Wɔ W' amandzehu wu yi,
Wo tsema a ɔmmbɔ adze yi?
Mo Wura, fa m' yɛ Wodze koraa;
Mma memmpa W' ara da;
Pa gu ma m' dɛ m' betsiatsia
W' anwanwa dɔ yi do!
 
. Muruwu a, mo Wura, bɛn me; 
Ao, yi Woho kyerɛ m'
Ao, tu faa bra bohwim me,
Bɛgye m' fi mbusu nsa;
Gyedzi ntom' mma n' enyiwa
Ontsim Jesus Wo do;
Na nyia owu gyedzi mu n'
Wo dɔ ma owu sɔnn.   Amen.

. Meremma nnkɔ ara da,
Gyedɛ mehu W'adom;
Ma mentse ndze dɛɛdɛw no,
Kasa, sɛ ennkɛfa akyɛ a;
Kasa, ma wonnya dza ayew,
Kasa, ma ewufo nnyan.

. Wo dɔ na meserɛ,
W'amandzehu dzi ma m';
Yaw na bɔgya a ikyii no,
Awerɛhow kɛse a idzii;
Meda W'ananadze, gye me,
Gyefo, gye nyia apon no.

. Ɔdɔ edzi dwuma no;
Ɔako, oedzi nyim koraa:
Ɔbo nye aweɔmfo n' yɛɛ kwa;
Christ efi samanadze:

. Wɔakrɔn hɛn Wura Christ wɔ sor;
Yedzi N'ekyir rokɔ hɔ;
Yɛtse dɛ Ɔno a, yɛbɔsoɛr;
Mbeamudua n' nye sor man n' hɛndze a:

. Ewuradze Christ asoɛr bio; 
Christ ebubu mpokyerɛ nyinam';
Tsie, abɔfo robɔ se,
Rotow ndwom wɔ sor daa daa:
                          Hallelujah!

. Ɔyɛ aperdzi a ɔyɛ hu,
Ber a nkwa na 'wu dzii aper;
Naaso nkwa dzii konyim nwanwa!
Owu n'ahendzi bɔɔ adze,
Wɔagye ne nsamu tum nyina;
Ne nyimpadua nko na aka;
No bɔr etu afebɔɔ.
	Alleluia

. N-tsi wɔmma yendzi afahyɛ n',
Ewuradze to nsa frɛ hɛn;
Christ ankasa nye hɛn enyigye
Na ewia a ɔhyerɛn hɛn do;
Ɔnam N'adom no do ma
Akoma nya onnyiewiei kan;
Bɔn anafua no etwa m'.
	Alleluia

. Siansian akra a wɔdeda Satan mpokyerɛ m'
Fa hɔn a wɔahwe ase nyina bra nkwa mu bio;
Fa W'enyim ne hyerɛn kyerɛ, ma aman nyina nhu;
Ma adze nkye hɛn bio, 'Wo na edze da pa ba.

. Jesus rihyia hɛn, ɔasoɛr efi nda m';
Ɔdze dɔ kyia hɛn, oyi suro na awerɛhow;
Ma asɔr no mfa enyigye mbɔ ose,
Osiandɛ Ewuradze tse ase, owu nnyi tum.

. Yɛnngye Wo kyim bio, o n-kwa Wura;
Boa hɛn na sɛ innyi mu a, ɔbra nnyɛ yie;
Fa Wo daa dɔ no yɛ hɛn konyimdzifo;
Fa hɛn twa Jordan kɔ wo sor fie hɔ sɔnn.

. Ɔko kɛse no abɔ adze; 
Afei hɛn Sahen edzi nyim;
Wɔnhyɛ ehurusi ndwom n' ase: 
	Alleluia!
 
. Owu hyehyɛɛ no dɔm petsee, 
Na Christ abɔ hɔn apetse;
Wɔmbɔ se ntow enyigye ndwom: 
	Alleluia!

. Aweɛhow ndaansa no etwam'; 
Ɔasoɛr konyim mu efi wum';  
Enyimnyam nka Hen tseasefo n'; 
	Alleluia!
 
. Ewuradze, W' amandzehu ntsi, 
Gye Wo nkowaa fi wu no bɔr mu,
Ma yeenya nkwa, yaatow Wo ndwom:  
	Alleluia!

. Hom mma hom enyi do, hom ntow ndwom;
Agyenkwa n' tse ase bio;
Owu dadzeban nyinara
Enntum annkora No.

. Nnyɛ ndɔmmum, ahomgye wɔ sor;
Nnyɛ awerɛhow; 'perdzi m' komm;
Ebɛda nn-kyerɛ dɛ ewu,
'Bɛtsena Christ mu nye ɔbra pa.

. Woana nye Enyimnyam Hen yi?
Ewuradze, 'nyimnyamfo tumfo n';
Ahotsewfo nye abɔfo Hen n';
Adze nyina do Nyame siarfo. 
Hallelujah!

. Abɔfo nhyɛ Gyefo ahenkyɛw;
Ɔdze empirenyimdze aba;
Wɔmfa No nsi tum egua n' do;
Ber a heaven rowosow yi,
Wɔnhyɛ N' ahenkyɛw! Gyefo no,
Ahemfo Hen no ahenkyɛw.

. Tsie dodow osebɔ kɛse n';
Tsie hɔn konyimdzi ndwom no;
Hwɛ, Jesus ekedzi sorsor;
Mbrɛ iyi si ma dɛw a!
Hom nhyɛ N' ahenkyɛw na hom nhua N',
'Hemfo Hen, ewuranom Wura!

. Hwɛ, W'ahom rehyɛ W'asɔr a ɔwɔ,
Mbeambea nyinara no ma;
Hyɛ mo so m'akoma ma, na
Minya pɛ W'adom ber yi;
Bra, Ɔwo enyimnyam Hen, bra,
Fa m'akoma yɛ Wo fie;
Tsena m', na Wo nko dzi hen hɔ
Dɛ Wo sor ahengua n' do!   Amen.

. Nyame N'afɔrbɔ Eguambaa,
Wɔdze hɛn bɔn nyina soaa Wo;
Enam ɔdɔ kɛse do na
Ebɔɔ werdam pa maa hɛn;
Wo nkorɔfo nyina enya bɔnfakyɛ,
Ɔnam Wo bɔgyaa no ntsi;
Woebue heaven abow n' petee;
Somdwee wɔ Nyame na nyimpa m'.

. Jesus, enyimnyam Hen, m-bo!
Ewɔ enyimnyam m' afebɔɔ;
Ɔsor dɔm nyinara sɔr Wo,
Etse Egya N'abanyimfa;
Ewɔ hɔ na idzi ma abɔn,
'Siesie tsenabew pa ma hɛn;
Idzi ma hɛn afebɔɔ, kɛpem
Dɛ yepue enyimnyam mu.

. DZI dɛw mbordo ara! Hɛn Pomfo no aba;
Kɔhwɛ N'adasoe, mbeamudua na Ne nda.
   Yi No ayɛw; bo Nyia wokum No no ho dawur;
   Yi No ayɛw; fa dɛw ka dɛ ɔtse ase bio.

. HƐN Sɔfopanyin dze N' akam,
No dɔ a ɔyɛ wu n' ho nsewhyɛ;
Ɔsɔɔw no enyimnyam mu no,
Kɛhɛɛn ɔsor krɔnkrɔnbea hɔ;
Ɔdze Ne yaw serɛ wɔ dua n' do,
Yi Noho kyerɛ Nyame ma me.

. M' Agyenkwa gyina ahengua n'enyim,
Ogyina dɛ m' Nyɛnko, Dzimafo;
Woekrukye me dzin wɔ Ne nsamu,
Ɔno na Egya n' tsie No daa;
Ber a m'kosɔw Jesus mbeamudua n' ho n',
Ɔtse bɔgya ne mpetsee no.

. Mubotum enya No tum mpaabɔ n'
Ho mbuae ha sesei ara mpo;
Ɔno ntsi metse ase sesei,
Meka dɛ ɔtse Nyame mu;
Ɔrennkyɛr, me kra a ɔwɔ N' nsamu n'
Begyina bea a me Kandzifo n' gyina.

. JESUS, yεba Wo hɔ,
Hεn enyi da Wo mboa do;
Wo nko nye hεn guandɔbea.
Ebrε hεn suro nyina adze;
Akoma biara ahomgye.
Ɔkra a oruwu biara nkwa.

. Yεdze akokodur
Krɔnkrɔn gye akatua n’;
W’enyimnyam dεw yε hεndzc,
Wo dɔ egyapadze nyina;
Afei yεsɔ sor turn hwε,
Yεnye  Wo dzi hen wɔ sor.

. Yeatow hen sekyε dzen
Wɔ twamutam no mu;
Hεn enyidado a ɔmmpa n’
Si pi wɔ Krɔnkrɔn -bea hɔ;
Yebedzi W'ekyir afow
Ekohu Nyame N’enyim.

. Ɔtse ase dze No dɔ hyira me,
Ɔtse ase, dzi ma me wɔ sor;
Ɔtse ase, nyɛn me kra daa daa;
Ɔtse ase, boame ohia ber m'.

. Hom Sahen se, Hyɛ dzen!
Ɔno a onyim hom berɛ;
Hom bɛberɛ dze; hom mbu n'anhwer;
Medzi nyim ama hom,
Konyimdzi no nye yi!
Wɔhwɛ hɛn gyedzi enyim;
Jesus ewu ama me nye wo;
Gye dzi na dzi konyim.

. Ɔba ntsɛm dɛ ɔbɔboa
Hɔn a woruhu amandze;
Dɛ ɔbɔboa ehiafo,
Mberɛwyɛfo enya ahoɔdzen;
Hɔn apensi adan ndwom;
Hɔn sum adan ekan,
Hɔn a hɔn akra ruwu n,
Wɔsom bo wɔ N'enyim.

. Ɔbɛba dɛ mpetsema
Abɔfɔw asaase;
Ɔdɔ, dɛw enyidar, nhyiren
Bedzi N'awoe enyim;
'Somdwee bedzi N'enyim kan
Abɔ No dawur yie;
Na tsenenee bɛtsen dɛ nsu,
Fi bepɔw do esian.

. Ahemfo bɔhwe N'enyim,
Dze sika, nduhuam aba;
Aman nyina bɔtonton No,
Nkorɔfo beyi N'ayɛw;
Mpaabɔ a ɔmmbɔ adze da
Bɔfow edu N'enyim;
N'ahendzi bɛyɛ kɛse,
Ɔnnkɔbɔ adze da.

Ma w' akoma nye wo ndze do; 
   Dzi dɛw, mese wo dɛ, Dzi dɛw. 
 
. Agyenkwa Christ dzi hen, 
Nokwar nye dɔ dzi wɔ n';
Ɔhoor hɛn ho fi no,
Ɔgyee egua wɔ sor:

. Enuanom Jesus yi
Ɔbɛsan aba;
Ɔdze N'Egya enyimnyam
Na N'abɔfo dɔm;
Wɔdze aman abɔtsir nyina
Bɛhyɛ N' ahenkyɛw;
Hɛn akoma gye No to m'
Dɛ ''Nyimnyam Hen ndɛ.

. Edze ndwuma ahyɛ Wo nkowaa nsa,
Ehyira hɔn mbɔdzen do;
Na hwɛ, Wo mu
Yehu dɔm pii,
Agyedzifo a atsew hɔn ho;
Ndzebɔnyɛfo a 'dze akyɛ hɔn
Yi hɔn Gyefo no ayɛw;
Wɔtow ndwom daa,
Asɛmpa ndwom n',
Dzi nyim wɔ W'ayamuyie mu.

. Ɔnnkɛkyɛr ɔkɔ no botwa,
Yebenyam aperdzi frankaa n,;
Atamfo a yeedzi hɔn do n'
Boguan efi akono;
Hom nkɔ kan, hom nntsetsew hom mu,
Hom ntsea m' ntow konyimdzi ndwom.

. Nyame adzekyee, bra!
Adze asa akyɛr;
Yesi nkrum wɔ hɛn mu,
Yesu wɔ hɛn bɔn ho;
O Anapa Woraba, twe bɛn;
O Tsenenee Ewia, pue na hyerɛn.

. Nyame adzekyee, bra!
Wiadze aberɛ aperdzi;
Aprandaa him akoko,
Nyimpa akoma werɛ how;
Nyame adzekyee, asomdwee da, bra,
Na ma akofo dede no ngyaa!

. Zion tse aweɔmfo ndwom no
Na n'akoma dzi dɛw papaapa;
Onyan, ɔsoɛr fi no sum mu;
Na no Wura sian ba enyimnyam mu,
N'adom nye No nokwardzi dzi mu;
No Woraba epue, ne Kan aba!
Bra, Ɔwo a woehyira Wo,
Nyame No dɔ Ba no;
Halleluya!
Yedzi W'ekyir kohu dan a 
Enye hɛn bedzidzi mu no.

. Afei ma ɔsor nyina ntonton Wo,
Nyimpa nye abɔfo ntow Wo ndwom;
Hom mfa sanku a ɔyɛ dɛw;
Hom mfa bobaa hyɛnhyɛnn nkɔ hɔ,
Beebi a yenye adwontofo a wonnwu,
Abɔfo a woetwa ahengua n' ho;
Enyi nnhunii, aso
So mpo nnyaa nntsee nn-siei,
Dza ɔyɛ hɛndze;
Naaso yedzi dɛw na yɛtow
Wo hɛn dɛw ho ndwom daa nyina.

. Woraba kan a ɔrepa no mu yehu dɛ adze rekye;
Nyimpa hɔn kandzea ayɛ kusuww wɔ adzekyee hyɛnhyɛn n' mu;
Na boka wimu regyegye ber a nsumaa mu gya rehyerɛn n'
Ma nyimpa akoma dze ɔpɛ kɛse rowosow yi.

. Orububu mpampi nyina egu, orubue kwan no mu;
Ɔrefrɛ N'abɔfoe no dɛ wombuebue adzekyee mbobow n';
Mbom ha abɔfo no yɛ nyimpa, nnyɛ ɔsor dze a 
wɔhyerɛn no a,
Na No nsordaafo akyen ndze nyɛ dɛ dza hɛn akoma bɔtow.

. Akoma biara n'esumasɛm;
Apɛdze na etumayɛdze;
Dza ɔbra mmpotsi ho nkyerɛ nyina
Da edzi dɛ onnsuro afɔbu.

. Wo daa ahendzi nnkɔbɔ adze;
Wo mfesi pi, yɛ dɛw, na nyaa;
W'asomdwee wiadze kɛse 'i mu
Nyiren kumaa biara hyerɛn.

. M'ENYI ehu Ewuradze Ne mbae no ho enyimnyam;
Orikyi nsa beebi a wɔdze ebufuw wenyin gu n o;
Oesian Ne nkrantsee hoɔharfo huuhu no n'enyinam no
No nokwar no ritsim.

. Oenya obɔ totorbɛnto a ɔnnkɛsam akofo ekyir da,
Ɔresa nyimpa akoma mu wɔ 
N'atsembugua no enyim;
O me kra, yɛ ntsɛm kɛma no mbuae;
M'anan, huruhuruw!
Hɛn Nyame rutu ntsen.

. Ɔhyɛɛ edwuma no ase n',
Nna wonnyaa nntsee Ne nka;
Sesei asɛm no etu ntsen
Na ɔretserɛw kɔ mbea pii;
Ogu do petse na onyin
Kɔ ahoɔdzen konyimdzi mu;
Obubu bɔn akoban,
Wosow hɛll aponkɛse n'.

. N' amandzehu ho nsɛnkyerɛdze 
Da ho ara wowɔ No ho;
Dza N' asomfo a wɔapon hɔn no
Dzi ho ehurusi daa n';
Yɛdze dɛw bɛn
Bɔhwɛ enyimnyam etua n'.

. Ɔnyɛ hɔ! nkorɔfo nyina mbu W' ntwɛr 
Wo domankoma ahengua n' enyim;
Gyefo, gye tum na enyimnyam no,
Gye ahendzi n' yɛ Wodze;
Alleluia!
Onnyiewiei Nyankopɔn, sian!

. Mma hom nnsuro, hom nntɔ bahaw;
Hom nko dɛ mbarimba;
Aman nyina bɔkotow Christ,
Nye hom atow ndwom yi.

. Ayewa mbobow n' ebuebue;
Ndadzeban n' ebuebue;
Hwɛ, Enyimnyam Hen no resen!
Mbeamudua n' edzi nyim.

. Wɔdze nsɛmpa n' ama obiara,
Naaso mpempem nnyaa nntsee koraa;
Obi annka a, aso wɔbɛtse?
Owura Tumfo, ka asɛm no;
Ka asɛm no; aman nyina mu,
Ma asɛmpa abɛn nhɛn;
Ngye wiadze nyina nkwagye
Dase nkesi wiadze ano.

. Ewiei no, W'asɔr dzi mu a,
Hɔn a eyi hɔn nyina bɛba m'
Nye hɔn Hen n' atsena 'nyimnyam mu,
Wɔakyekyer abɔnsam na bɔn;
Osu, ɔkɔm awerɛhow,
Owu na yaw nnyi hɔ bio;
Hwɛ! W'asɔr so roweɔn ara;
Owur Jesus, bedzi hen!

. Wo ho yɛ fɛw kyɛn adasa nyina,
Idzi mu wɔ frɔdɔɔ mu so;
W'anomu nsɛm yɛ adom ara nko,
Na ɔdɔ ahyɛ W'akoma m' ma;
Nyame Siarfo! Yɛkotow Wo,
Na yɛka dɛ amayɛ dzi wɔ W'.

. Bra na bɛyɛ Wo tsenenee ndwuma,
Na mma Wo berɛ no nnyɛ gyan;
Ma Wo mbeamudua no konyimdzi n'
Ntserɛw wɔ wiadze mbea nyina;
Kɔ kan konyimdzi m' wɔ wiadze
Na dzi hen akoma nyina mu.  Amen.

. Nkorɔfo na ngyirama mpem nyina 
Dze No dɔ ho ndwom dɛɛdɛw mu;
Na mbofra so ma hɔn ndze do,
Wɔtow Hosanna ma Ne dzin.

. Mbrɛ odzi hen n', nhyira ahyɛ ma, 
Wotu adaduafo apo;
Afonafo nya daa ahomka;
Na ehiafo so, wohyira hɔn.

. EWURADZE, Yɛgye dzi dɛ
'Dze asomafo bɔhyɛ n' ama hɛn;
Yɛhwɛ Pentecost tum no kwan,
Sunsum Krɔnkrɔn a edze fi sor n';

. Yɛabɔ ɔnosɛɛ ehyia ha
Rotweɔn adom anohoba n';
Hɛn Wura a owui n' N'atɔdze;
Sunsum Krɔnkrɔn, bɛhyɛ ha ma.

. Hwɛ, hɛn akra per hwehwɛ Wo,
Rotweɔn dɛ ibesian daadze;
Kenyan Wo gya no wɔ hɛn mu;
Na bɛtsena akoma biara m'. Amen.

. Nyame, 'domankoma Nyame,
Ɔnye adasa tsena;
Dze nyimpa yɛ N'atsenae;
Abɛtsena nyimpa mu.

. Sunsum Krɔnkrɔn, kenyan m'akoma,
Dzi dase dɛ wɔawo m'fofor;
Fa ogya bonuma me sesei
Amma W'akyɛdze aannyɛ gyan,
Munnkotum atsena bɔnfakyɛ m' daa;
M'bɛyɛ dɛn akɔ heaven hɔ?

. Sunsum no egua nnyi ekyir,
Na ɔbɛn hɛn wɔ ha ara;
Ɔwɔ akoma biara mu;
Na ɔtweɔn dɛ wobohu N'.

. Sunsum fotufo, kyerɛ hɛn kwan;
Dua aperdzi do kyerɛkyerɛ hɛn 
Ma yennya sor ahenkyɛw;
'Kokodur Sunsum, fa Wo tum
Ma hɛn wɔ hɛn nsɔhwɛ ber mu,
Na ɔmma yengyaa bɔn yɛ.

. Sunsum Krɔnkrɔn, Nyame dɛw,
Fa dɛw hyɛ m'akoma mu;
Mobɔtow ndwom wɔ sar do;
Nsunyiwa, O Nsubura, pem daa.   Amen.

. Nyame Sunsum, tsie hɛn mpaabɔ; 
Yɛ wiadze a 'ayew Wo fie;
Fa W' adom No tum nyina sian;
Bra, Sunsum kɛse, bra.   Amen.

. NDZEMBA nyina nyi Ewuradze ayɛw;
Sor na asaase, po na wimu,
Eyɛe hyɛɛ Woho enyimnyam,
Dze daa Wo kɛseyɛ edzi
Yɛdze som nyina brɛ Wo;
Yɛnye adze nyina yi W'ayɛw.

. Adze nyina yi W'ayɛw 'nago,
Wɔtow kan adwom kommyɛ mu;
Woyi W'ayɛw 'dzekyee nyina,
Ewiaber wɔkyerɛ Wo tum;
Ber na bea riyi W'ayɛw,
Yɛnye adze nyina yi W'ayɛw.

. Nyame Sunsum, tsie hɛn mpaabɔ,
Yɛ wiadze a ayew Wo fie;
Fa W'adom No tum nyina sian;
Bra, Sunsum kɛse, bra.   Amen.

. Sunsum Brɛfo, nye me ntsena!
Emi so m' bɛyɛ brɛfo;
M'akoma bɔmonsom dɛ nhyiren
Wɔ nsɔhwɛber sunkamm n' mu;
Obobue ber a ewia abɔ,
Na m' benya No dɔ no huam.

. Ɔhyew a wɔammbɔ farbaa,
Kyigyinafo a Egya n' dze maa hɛn,
Bura na gya krɔnkrɔn mprɛnsa;
Fa sor dɔ kenyan hɛn akoma;
Bra, na fa Wo ngo krɔnkrɔn no
Bɛtsew hɛn ho ber a yɛtow ndwom.

. Yɛ ndzɛmba fofor hyɛ pɛ do,
Brɛ hɛn akra asoɔdzenfo adze;
Ma hɛn nsa nka daa nokwar no,
Yɛmfa hɛn gyedzi nyɛ edwuma;
Fa Woho ma hɛn ma yenhu,
Egya na Ba no wɔ Wo mu.

. Ͻwo a eyɛ ͻdͻ krͻnkrͻn,
Ma hɛn W’akyɛdze nyina;
Mma mmfi hɛn nkyɛn ara da;
Sunsum Krͻnkrͻn, tsie hɛn.

. Ku hɛn akͻndͻbͻn nyina;
Hyɛ hɛn asoadzen pɛ do;
Yesérɛ W’ nya abotar ma hɛn:
Sunsum Krͻnkrͻn, tsie hɛn.

. Metakyeer edziban bɔn ho;
Masɔ ahwɛ dɛ Ewuradze ye;
Mema m'enyi do hwɛ wimu
Dze hwɛ dza Bɔadze bɛma.

. Wiadze dadwen hyɛ som ma;
Botae hun ka dwumadzi hyɛ,
Ahokyerɛ, ber a Nyame bɛn;
Akwadwer, ber a sum mba wu.

. Abͻnfo Wura, guar hɛn;
Yɛyar, yeafona, hyɛ hɛn dzen;
Yɛayew, gyedɛ etsen hɛn,
’Wérɛkyekyer Nyame.

. Mehaahaa bisa Wo dodow;
Sor ahom a ͻyɛ dzen yie,
Twe m’ pue ahotͻ dɛɛdɛw mu
Kɛpem dɛ me kra ayɛ Wodze;
‘Korsa po bun emunam mo do,
Na mayew Wo kokrokoyɛ m’.

. AMANAMAN, hom mfa dew nkotow 
Jehova ahengua huuhu enyim;
Hom nhu Ewuradze nko dɛ Nyame;
Ɔno na ɔbɔ na ono na Osɛɛ.

. N'ahentum no, onnhia hɛn mboa;
Ɔdze dɛtse nween hɛn nyimpa.
Yɛtse dɛ nguan a yɛtɔɔ gon n';
Ɔdze hɛn baa nguankuw n'mu bio.

. Ofi sor bɛgyee hɔn a wɔahera nkwa;
Abɔn, hom mbra mbɛgye Jesus dzin ndzi;
Ɔdze bɔn kyɛ, ɔma obiara fahodzi;
Sɛ bɔn nye w'adzesoa a; O bra Me nkyɛn ha!

. Abɔnfo, hom ngye nsɛmpa n' ndzi,
Jesus rebɛgye hom akra!
Jesus aba, hom Wura nye no;
Hom nyina benya fakyɛ wɔ N' mu,
Nyia ɔpɛ biara benya nkwa;
Nyimpa yi da ho gye abɔn.

. Enyimnyam nka Nyame! Ɔayɛ adze kɛse!
Ɔdɔɔ wiadze ara ma ɔdze N' Ba maa hɛn;
Ɔno a ɔdze No nkwa bɔɔ werdam maa abɔn,
Na obuee nkwa abotsen dɛ obiara nhɛn mu;

. TSIE ! Nsɛmpa ndze no regyegye;
Christ atseetsee dua no do;
Ehumbͻbͻr nsu repem weͻͻ;
’Biara nya adorn bafuu kwa.
Nkyii, bͻnyɛnyi,
Hwɛ Nyia owui maa wo No.

. Ao, guan kͻ ekyir koko no do!
Nkyii hyɛ ase weͻn na sͻr;
Christ frɛ wo nsunyiwa no ho;
Bra bͻhohor wo bͻn no,
Mma nnyɛ ekyim,
Bra N‘ hͻ bér a ibotum yi.

. Adom repem de esutsen;
Ͻama ͻpepé enya bi;
Ͻda ho ara repem krͻngyee
Fi Agyenkwa mfe m‘ ‘piratua m’:
’Biara nnkɛehéra;
Christ ewu, hom benya nkwa.

. YƐATSE enyigye ndze bi;
Christ gye nkwa!
Ma enyigyesɛm yi mpetse;
Christ gye nkwa!
Fa asɛm no kɔ mbea nyina,
Fow mbepɔw na twa po so;
Hom nduom! Ewuradze ndze nye n';
Christ gye nkwa!

. Tow ndwom ma ɔmbor ɔsa n' do;
Christ gye nkwa!
No wu nye onnyiewie nkwa ntsi
Christ gye nkwa
Tow no bɔkɔɔ wɔ sum no m';
Ber a akoma hwehwɛ ehumbɔbɔr;
Tow konyim wɔ owumaa do;
Christ gye nkwa!

. Hom mma ehum no ndze kɛse;
Christ gye nkwa!
Aman nyina mbɔ ose sesei;
Christ gye nkwa!
Tsea m', nkwagye a odzi mu, wɔnntɔ,
'Dze ma wiadze mbea nyina-
Hɛn konyimdzi ndwom nye yi;
Christ gye nkwa!

. OBIARA a ͻtse n‘, ͻmma ndze no do!
Mfa nhyira nsɛmpa no ntsérɛw wiadze nyina;
Tsérɛw ’nyigyesɛm wͻ mbea a nyimpa du n’ nyina:

Obiara a ͻpɛ n’ ͻmbra.
    Obiara a ͻpɛ n’! Obiara a ͻpɛ n’! 
    Ͻmbͻ dawur n' wͻ mbͻnsa na
    nkokwaa do;
	Egya dͻfo no refrɛ’ akobͻfo fie;
	Obiara a ͻpɛ n’ ͻmbra.
    
. Obi a ͻreba n’ mma ͻnnyɛ ekyim,
Bér a abow no ebuei yi hɛn mu ntsɛntsɛm;
Jesus nye nokwar no na nkwa kwan no;
Obiara a ͻpɛ n’ ͻmbra. '

. AKRA 'werɛfo a hom kyin
Fi nhyira finimfin no,
Hom nkɔ Jesu a wɔsɛɛn N' hɔ,
Hom nguan nkɔ N'epirakur ho;
Hom ntɔ ahosan nsu n' mu;
Hom nsoɛr nkɔ Nyame nkwa mu.

. Hwehwɛ asomdwee kwan Christ mu,
Asomdwee a onnyi kabea;
Ne yaw no ma w' ahotɔ,
Ne pen a ɔdze ruwu ma w' nkwa;
Ma N'asehwe no mpegya w',
Ma Christ nyɛ wo adze nyina.

. O hom ngye nokwasɛm n' ndzi;
Nyame dze Ne Ba ama hom,
Afei hom so enyi bɛgye;
Hom nnya sor nkwa wɔ ase,
Hom ntsena sor abrabɔ n' mu,
Wɔ enyimnaym dɔ asetsena mu.

. Mma mmpa mo ho, Agyenkwa brɛfo, 
Ma mondɔ Wo na mentar Wo;
Mo kɔn adɔ W' enyimtsewee;
Ber a 'refrɛ yi frɛ me so,

. Bra, ɔbɛma W' ahomgye; 
Twer No: N' asɛm si no pi:
Ɔgye abɔn mu abɔn;
Christ ɔgye ndzebɔnyɛfo.

. M' akoma mmubu me fɔ bio, 
Mo ho san wɔ mbra n' enyim;
Nyia ɔhoor mo ho fi no
Apata mbra no koraa.
 
. Christ ɔgye ndzebɔnyɛfo, 
Emi mpo a mo bɔn dɔɔ so;
Me nkekae nyinaa botu;
Ɔnye m' bɛhɛn sor man mu.

. Abɔn, 'kɔbesaefo, hom mbra, 
Bahatɔfo, epirafo,
Jesus rotweɔn agye hom nkwa;
Tsema na tum ahyɛ N' ma;
Ɔyɛ Tumfo
Ɔpɛ, mma hom nngye kyim bio.

. Hom mbra, hom a hom kɔn ebu, 
Hom a asehwe epira hom;
Sɛ hom rotweɔn ayɛ yie ana a,
Hom nnkɛba dabiarada;
Nnyɛ atsenenee a,
Abɔn na Jesus bɛfrɛe.

. Guanhwɛfo a owui dze gyee No nguan;
Abahatͻfo a wͻaba asesa
Etwa Wo ho ehyia akwan nyina do;
Rotweͻn bͻnfakyɛ wͻ Jesus N’adom mu.

. Efurafo nam Jesus dzin mu hu adze,
Wohu hͻn Wura, ka Eguambaa No do;
Mpakye nantsew, tutu mbirika, si mpire;
Mmum kasa ka Jesus N’ adom no ho, asɛm.

. Etsitsifo tse N’akomatͻm’ ndze n’,
Ͻma wodzi dɛw wͻ Jesus hͻn wura m’;
Wͻdze w’ bͻn akyɛ wo, wͻagye w’ ato mu;
Wotsie na sor pue wͻ hͻn akoma mu.

. ONNYIEWIEI Nyame, yɛma hɛn
Akoma do tow ndwom yi W' ayɛw;
Wo ndwuma a ɔwɔ asaase nyina tonton W',
 Yɛsom Wo , nyimpa nyina Ewuradze;
Hɛn domankoma Egya nye Wo,
Yɛkotow wɔ W'ahengua enyim.

. Atɔfo nyimnyam kuw ne tsir,
Wɔdze Wo hoahoa hɔnho daa;
Asɔr a ɔwɔ wiadze afanan nyina,
Yi no sor Farbaa no ayɛw;
Na wɔnye ahengua ho dɔm no
Per tow ndwom ma Ɔkorsa no.

. Ewuradze, W'eduokron akron n' wɔ ha;
Ana wɔnndɔɔ so mma Wo?
Guanhwɛfo no buaa dɛ, Medze yinom
Atɔ dɔnsuar efi me nkyɛn;
Kaansa kwan no kyeakyea, yɛ kronn mpo a,
Mokɔ sar no do kɔhwehwɛ Mo nguan.

. Sor bobɔ mu wɔ akoko nyina do,
Na mbotantsim sorɔnsorɔmbea
Hɔ na su fii kɔr sor pon ano;
Dzi dɛw, mehu Mo guan no,
Abɔfo tseatseaa mu wɔ ahengua n'ho;
Dzi dɛw, Ewuradze dze no reba.

. Tsenenee Ewia no dze ayarsa;
Epue, ahyerɛn wͻ mo do,
Mo honam mu ahom asa;
Na me kra no nkwa fi Wo hͻ:
Mo mboa nyina wͻakora n’ sor.
Wo su na Wo dzin nye Ͻdͻ.

. Mayɛ apakye mpo a, mo bo dwe
Kesi ͻbra kwantsiaa yi ewiei;
M’awerɛhow na me mberɛwyɛ mu
Wo nko W’ nkyɛn na minya ahoͻdzen;
‘Nngya me ma minnkyinkyin gyan kwa,
Wo su na Wo dzin nye Ͻdͻ.

. Ͻda ntsi Ͻwo wui maa me!
M’akoma tse W’ano wasa;
Adze akye ma sum apa,
Wiadze nyina eyɛ ͻdͻ krͻnn;
Ihu nyimpa nyina mbͻbͻr:
Wo su na Wo dzin nye Ͻdͻ.

. Agyenkwa, minyim mbrɛ etse,
Jesus, ͻbͻn bafan Adamfo;
Mma mmfi me nkyɛn adzesaaber mpo,
Tsena na dͻ me kͻ ewiei;
Wo mbͻbͻrhu mmpa ara da,
Wo su na Wo dzin nye Ͻdͻ

. Ɔwo 'nnhom, emmpɛ ntsɛm, eyɛ kan nwanwa;
Innhia hwee, emmpɛ hwee, idzi hen tum mu;
Wo pɛrpɛr dɛ bepɔw a ɔkrɔn kɔ sor,
Wo fua yɛ ayamuyie na dɔ nsunyiwa.

. Ema obiara nkwa, akɛse na nkumaa;
Na nkwa nyina ewɔ mu, nokwar nkwa nye Wo;
Yefifir yɛ prɔmprɔm dɛ ndua do nhaban,
Yenyinyam, yewuwu; Ɔwo nnsakyer da.

. Egya Onyimnyamfo, Kan Egya mapa;
W'abɔfo hyɛ kata hɔn enyim tonton Wo;
Enyimnyam nyina sɛ Wo; boa hɛn ma yenhu;
Kan fɛɛfɛw ara na ɔdze Wo suma hɛn.

. Nkyii suo mo mu, na mayɛ mbérɛw, ,
Mowͻ awérɛhyɛm’ wͻ m’abagura m’;
Kasa nhyira m’ kyérɛ m’akoma,
Me mprempren mpaabͻ mpuhim Wo;
Kasa, ͻno nnkefi ha akͻ, 
Ka kyérɛ m’, sɛ Wo dzin nye Ͻda a.

. Ͻdͻ a ! Ͻdͻ a ! Iwui maa me!
Metse dɛ ’wasa m’akoma m’;
Adze kye, sunsum twa m’ hwew hwew,
Awͻmbea Ͻdͻ mapa nye Wo;
Ihu emi na obiara mbͻbͻr:
Wo su na Wo dzin nye Ͻdͻ.

. Anago m' yaw akɔ do akyɛr;
Wipuei bɛbrɛ hɛn kan;
Nyame bɛba, na yɛbɔsoɛr
Enyigye m' wɔ n'enyim.

. Afei mehu dɛ mankasa
Munnkotum afata ama Wo;
Ntsi migyaa ne nyina m' ma Wo;
Edwuma no yɛ Wo nko dze.

. Bɔn a mayɛ no wɔ adwen, nyɛe
Na kasa mu aka mo ho;
Meserɛ Wo bɔgyaa ne fakyɛ;
Christ a iwui, maba!

. Ɔwo nyim me yaw na suro,
W'adom na me mfe a masɛɛ;
Afei fa nyinsu tsew mo ho;
 Christ a iwui, maba!

. Guar m' na hohor me nkekaaba,
Mma mo bɔn biara nnka mo ho;
Yaw mu mpo na mo ho san yie;
Christ a iwui, maba!

. Inyim mbrɛ ibesi dze m' asan,
Na agye mo sunsum a ahera;
Wo nokwar ehumbɔbɔr ntsi,
Fa kyɛ m' na mma mennyɛ bɔn bio;
Yɛ mo sunsum pirafo edur,
Na yɛ m'akoma mpaabɔ fie.

. Ma ɔbo akoma nyɛ dɛ honam,
Yi bɔn nkataenyim no fi hɔ;
Fa Wo bɔgyaa guar m'akoma,
Dua Wo dɔ no do yi fi hɔ;
Hyɛ etuatsew akoma yi do,
Yɛ no botoo, yɛ no fofor.

. Fa Wo Sunsum ka m'enyim
Ma mo bɔn nyina nda edzi,
Bɔn a otsia Wo kan na dɔ;
Dza ɔbɔɔ me Nyame mbeamudua m' n',
Ma munhu na mentse nka;
W'adehye bɔgya n' mpem bio.

. Ma mumbopue W'enyim ara
Dɛ towgyenyi bɔbɔfo n',
Memmfata dɛ mebɛn Wo;
Bɔ m'akoko a ɔnnsɛ yi do,
Bɔnyɛnyi totɔserɛ dɛ;
Nyankopɔn, hu me mbɔbɔr!

. O kaa me korakora,
Ber a menam 'wu bɔnsa mu;
Ma munhu mpata bɔgya n';
Sɛ m'ahoɔdzen nyina sa a;
Ma me kra a ɔabɔm yi nhu
Jesus a wɔ bɔɔ N' mbeamudua m' n'!   Amen.

. JESUS, sɛ etse dɛmara a,
Sɛ W'anohoba nyina tsim hɔ a,
Ma W'ahendzi mbra m'akoma m';
Yɛ m' 'dzefo na meyɛ hianyi;
Fa W'akoradze nyina ma me,
Minnya sor ahenman mo mu.

. Ehyira hɔn a hɔn werɛ ahow;
Na hwɛ, daa meka Wo ho mmɔn;
Munnkotum ahom ara da
Kɛpem dɛ 'bɛma m' ahomgye;
Ɔwo a eyɛ asomdwee Hen n' bɛba
Na meenya Ɔwerɛkyekyefo n'.

. Ewuradze, sɛ etse me yaw a,
Mifi mo mu bɔ mpaa a tsie;
Tsie W' Sunsum Ne ntsea m' m'akoma m',
Hyɛ dza me kra reka no nsew;
Ma m'apensi no ho mbuae pa
Na kyerɛ dɛ Ɔwo na emi yɛ kor.

. Hyerɛn W'edwuma do na pam sum,
Hyerɛn Wo kan mu ama meehu;
Se me kra dɛ: Wo kan aba,
Nyame enyimnyan ahyerɛn wo do,
W'akodzi nye awerɛhow etwa m';
Ma w'enyi do na 'nnkosu bio!.

. Medze akomá a yaw ahyɛ n' má, 
Ewuradze na merefrɛ Wo;
W'adom ehumbɔbɔr ká pii;
Me Nyankopɔn, hu me mbɔbɔr.

. Motwe me nsa hwe mo bo do, 
Afɔdzi á ɔyɛ dur ahyɛ m' do;
Christ na Ne mbeamudua nye mo sú;
Me Nyankopɔn, hu me mbɔbɔr.

. Migyina ekyir nyinsu egur m' 
Munntum mma m'enyi do wɔ sor;
Wo na ihu me yaw nyina;
Me Nyankopɔn, hu me mbɔbɔr.

. Nyɛ ayamuyie na ndzepa a mayɛ 
Na obotum etua bɔn kor kaw;
Calvary nkotoo na muguan kɔ
Me Nyankopɔn, hu me mbɔbɔr.

. Munnkosuro m'atamfo;
Mirinngyaa mu mma ɔhaw, 
Mennkɛma awerɛhow ahyɛ mo do;
Ibetsie me mpaabɔ.

. OHO, nnyɛ abagura mu
Na meba W' hɔ;
Oho, nnyɛ ekyingye mu
Na mubu ntwɛr;
Bɔn ebu mo do dze,
'So 'yi nye m' ntotɔserɛ;
Jesus ewu.

. Nokwafo, pɛrpɛr nye W',
'Dze kyɛ obiara;
Dɔfo yamuyiefo nye W';
'Frɛ abɔbɔfo;
Owura, ma Wo bɔgyaa n',
Nyame Eguambaa bɔgyaa n',
Ɔmpem me kra m'.

. Nyew, ’Wo na ibeyi ano ama m’, tsénenee Wura:
Ndzépa nyina Wodzé a, medze yɛ akatua;
Wodze nsoɛ kyɛw a, medze sika' ahenkyɛw a;
Minya nkwa, Ͻwo dze Wo nkwa ato hͻ.

. Kaw a medze W’ yi murunntum nntua ho hwee;
Naaso ma dza ͻwͻ m’akoma m’ biara
Mary ’kyɛdze n', ma mo som nkyérɛ;
Akyɛ m’ dza  ͻso ’i, mo so m’ dͻ nyɛ kɛse.   Amen.

. Fa asomdwee a ɔnnsesa da
Hyɛ m'akoma mu ma ɔnhom;
Ma m'ekyimakyima nyina ntwa,
Na mma ommfi Wo nkyɛn ara bio;
Na ma monsɔ W'ayamuyie nhwɛ,
Ma mentsena Wo dɔ mu daa.

. Agyenkwa n' gyina hɔ ma m';
N'etua ɔkyerɔ tserɔw Ne nsamu,
Minyim dɔ Nyame nye ɔdɔ;
Jesus tse ase da ho dɔ m'.

. Meserɛ dɛ hu me mbɔbɔr;
Hwɛ me kra na frɛ no bra;
Ma ɔbo no ndan honam,
Hwɛ na bubu m'akoma.

. Siarfo nye nyia ohu nyansa,
Nyia ɔdze n' sie n' nya siar mbordo;
Odzi wɔ N', ɔbɛyɛ N'dze daa;
Nyansa, Christ na Sor yɛ adze kor.

. Migyina ha dɛ woepira m',
Mema m'enyi do hwɛ W';
M'awerɛhow, me yaw seradze,
W'adom bɛn me daa nyina;
Dɛ mbrɛ etse ndeda no,
Etse dɛmara daapem nyina.

. Ewuradze, menndze hwee a
Medze bɔtɔ W'adom;
Meyɛ hianyi dze naaso,
Mma memmfa nsapan nnkɔ;
Meyɛ huntuma nye nso,
Me ndzeyɛɛ nyina yɛ bɔn nko.

. SOƐR, me kra, soɛr gyina,
Tow w'afɔdzi suro gu;
Na emi ntsi na okyii
No bɔgyaa dze bɔɔ afɔr;
'Dzimafo gyina 'hengua n'enyim, 
Ɔakyerɛw me dzin wɔ Ne nsa ho.

. Ɔtse ase wɔ sor hɔ,
Odzi ma me wɔ hɔ;
Ɔdze No nkwagye dɔ
Nye No bɔgyaa serɛ;
Bɔgya a ɔpon adasa nyina n'
Petse adom ahengua n' ho.

. Egya n' tsie Ne Ba a
Ɔasera No ngo N' mpaabɔ;
N'abadaa burbur No,
Onntum mmfi Ne Ba n' nkyɛn;
No Sunsum ma bɔgya no mbuae,
Dɛ Nyame awo me ɔba.

. Menye Nyame abɔ m',
Metse Ne fakyɛ ndze n';
Ɔdze m' ayɛ Ne ba,
Dɛm ntsi munnsuro hwee;
Medze awerɛhyɛm' pinkyɛn;
Metsea m', Egya, Abba, Egya!

. JESUS, ndzebɔnyɛfo Adamfo,
Midzi W'ekyir a, mutu ehu;
Kenyan enyimnyam ko n';
Menya sor awerɛhyɛmu,
Medze gyedzi krɔnkrɔn suo mu;
Ɔwo nye me daa nkwa.

. N'adom nye nokwardzi dɔɔ so,
Ɔpɛ dɛ adasa asehwefo
Bɛsakyer enya nkwa;
Ne fakyɛ nye adom, ɔdze kyɛ;
Hɛn mfom na emumuyɛ nyina
Nyame dze kyɛ hɛn kwa.

. Ohu mpempem mbɔbɔr daa nyina,
Okyin hwehwɛ oguan a ɔayew n',
Na ɔdze no san ba fie;
Ɔkra biara nye dɛm oguan n';
Ewuradze Jesus, meserɛ Wo,
Bra bɛfa me kɔ ntsɛm.  Amen.

. Mber pii mo sunsum daduanyi
Daa bɔn mpokyerɛ na anago sum m';
W'enyiwa toow kan nserɛmɛn
Gyegyee fiadze hɔ, minyanee;
Mo mpokyerɛ gui, minyaa ahotɔ,
Mifiir edzi, midzii W'ekyir.

. Afei munnsuro afɔbu bi;
Jesus, No mu dze nyina medze a;
Metse No mu, me Tseasefo a
Ɔdze sor tsenenee efura m',
Medze 'kokodur bɛn ''hɛngua n',
Nam Christ do gye ahenkyɛw no.

. M'afɔbu efi mo do kɔ koraa,
Jesus nko na onyim siantsir;
Me kra ahyɛ nkwa nye nkwagye atar;
Jesus gye me nkwa.

. Dza hɛn Wura hyɛ hɛn n',
Yɛdze enyigye yɛ;
N'asɛmpa krɔnkrɔn no kyerɛ hɛn;
Yetsia N'anamɔn mu.    Amen.

. Ɔsor Egya a Wo dɔ kɛse n'
Abɔ werdam ama hɛn kra,
Abɔn yɛkotow W' egua enyim;
Wo bɔnfakyɛ dɔ n' fa dom hɛn.
 
. Ba Tumfo, Asɛm a ɔbrae, 
Hɛn Nkɔnhyɛnyi, Sɔfo, Pomfo,
Abɔn yɛkotow W' egua enyim;
Wo nkwagye adom n', fa dom hɛn.
 
. Sunsum Bɛkyebo a W' ahom ma 
Wɔgye kra fi bɔn nsa na wum',
Abɔn yɛkotow W' egua enyim;
Wo nkwahwea tum no, fa dom hɛn.
 
. Krɔnkrɔn mprɛnsa, Egya, Sunsum Ba; 
Nyametsir nwanwa, Ɔkorsa,
Abɔn yɛkotow W' egua enyim;
Adom, fafir, nkwa, fa dom hɛn.    Amen.

. Megye Nyame na N'asɛm to m';
M'akenkan dɛ Christ wui gyee me;
Metse nka wɔ m'akoma m' dɛ
No ho hia m' dɛ m'Agyenkwa.

. Yɛpɛ dɛ yɛyɛ Wodze koraa;
Gye hɛn afɔrbɔdze;
Ɔwo na ebɔɔ hɛn, gye hɛn nkwa,
Yɛdze hɛnho ma Wo.

. M' Agyenkwa! m'bɛyɛ dɛn etua 
Me kaw kɛse a medze Wo yi?
Ma dza mowɔ na metse nyina,
Nkyerɛ W'enyimnyam nyina daapem.
 
. Munntum mma Wo kɛse biara; 
Munntum nndzi dwuma kɛse mma W';
Kyerɛw nndzi dwuma kɛse mma W';
Gu m'akoma do afebɔɔ. Amen.

. MA m' gyedzi a otutu nkokwaa,
Na ɔma ne nyinara da fɛmm;
Ma me mbofra dɔ akoma a
Ɔpɛ dɛ osi Wo fie fofor;
Wo dɔ mfa m'akoma ndɔmmum,
Ɔmfa me kra bɔbɔfo 'i koraa.

. Mepɛ dɛ mofow ber pa a ɔsɛ m',
Matsena ase akyɛr yi ho;
Mahwer me mber pii wɔ hɔn a
Wonnyaa nnhun Agyenkwa pa n' ho;
Mibedzi dwuma yi prɛko,
M'ahomgu ayɛ Wo dɔ nko,

. Edze Wo nkwa maa me; 
Mo Wura, Wo bɔgyaa kyii
Ama aapon emi
Na meefi wum' masoɛr;
Edze Wo nkwa maa me:
'Midze, mama W' ebɛn?

. Ɔwo edze bɔnfakyɛ 
Na dɔ fi sor aba;
N-kwagye a odzi mu pii,
Edze ne nyina ama me;
Akyɛ me adze pii;
Mo so makyɛ W' ebɛn?

. Dza mekyekyer ndɛ yi nko hɔ daa,
Wɔ gyedzi nye Christ Nyimpadua mu;
N'esubɔ wɔ Esutsen Jordan mu;
Ne mbeamudua do wu ma me nkwagye;
No mpuei fi owumaa no mu;
No sorkɔ kwan do akwantu;
Ne ba wɔ atsɛmbu da mu;
Medze kyekyer moho ndɛ da 'i.

. Medze moho ma W' afebɔɔ, 
Mowɔ hɔ ma Wo som nko;
Mma mimmfi Wo nkyɛn ara da;
Ma Wo suban mbra mo do.	 Amen.

. Ewuradze, W'akowaa pa nye me;
Dza mowɔ nyina Wodze a;
Wɔawo m' ato W'ebusua mu,
Na apon m' ayɛ Wodze.

. Wo nsa na ɔyɛɛ m', Wo nsa so na
Oeyi m' efi bɔn mu;
Ehumbɔbɔr a ɔgyee me n';
Adwer m' dzen wɔ Wo mu.

. Nyame, W’ehumbɔbɔr tsim daa;
Onnyiewiei nokwar dwir W'asɛm: 
	Hallelujah!

. BƐKYEBO Nyame, m'akoma
Tsim Wo do;
Masan m' eyi apɛdze afebɔɔ;
Christ yɛ m' dze,
Ɔno nye mo Sɔfoe na m' Hen,
Ɔno na ɔdze mo nkwagye bae;
Ber a mugu a hom yi m' bɔtow;
Christ yɛ m' dze.

. No m' muhu Nyametsir ne hyerɛn;
Christ yɛ m'dze,
Ɔno nye Ɔhempɔn Krɔnkrɔn no;
Christ yɛ m'dze,
Egya No Dɔba a ɔdɔ No,
Nyia ɔnye No bɔ mu dzi Hen,
Nyia ɔbɔɔ werdam maa adasa;
Christ yɛ m'dze.

. Menantsew hwiihwii
Kɔ sor aponto ase;
Ɔno nye emudzi; ne dɛw no so dze,
Mobɔsɔ mahwɛ;
M'bohu dɛ mbrɛ ɔtse,
Sor hɔ wɔ Jesus No dɔ nwanwa no mu.

. Dɛm ahotɔ n' yɛ m'dze,
Ber a minyaa enyimpa n'
Wɔ Eguambaa No bɔgyaa no mu;
M'akoma gyee no dzii,
Onyaa enyigye kɛse;
Jesus nko Ne dzin mu heaven bi a!

. Foforyɛfo krɔnkrɔn, mihyira W';
Mikyia W'edzifirii;
Modɔ Wo wɔ W'ahoɔfɛw mu
Wɔ mfunoma yi ho.

. Fa ɔbra mber fɛɛfɛw brɛ No,
Ɔbɛma ayɛ fɛw mbordo;
Fa w'ahom kakra n' ma No,
Ɔbɛtsew w'ahoɔdzen ho;
Fa w'ehiasɛm to N'enyim,
Na ɔbɛma wo w'ehiadze.

. Mema m'Ebenezer do dɛ
Ha na aboa me ebodu;
Na mowɔ awerɛhyɛmu dɛ
Ɔwo dze m' bodu fie sɔnn;
Meyewee fii Nyame nguan mu,
Na Jesus dze me baa fie;
Ɔgyee me fii mbusu mu so,
No bɔgyaa apata mo bɔn.

. Ɔwo nye ebùn a wonndù ase;
Fa me hyɛ W’adom po no mu!
Nyansa mapa nnyi m’akoma m’;
Fa Wo dɔ no twa mo ho hyia.

. M'Agyenkwa Jesus nye me bambɔ pa;
Motwer N'asɛm ntsi mirimmfi Ne nkyɛn;
Menya N'enyim enyimpa ntsi ɔbɛyɛ biribia 'a;
Me Hen na m'Agyenkwa bɛyɛ me fofor.

. Sɛ mo werɛ fir No na mikyinkyin mpo a,
Beebiara a m'bɔkɔ n' ɔda ho dɔ me;
Mutu mbirika san kɔ No dɔ abaw m;
Ber a mekaa dɛ saana Jesus dɔ me.

. Ahobrɛdze koraa, ne nyina adwe, 
Menya Agyenkwam' ahomka nye siar;
Moroweɔn, rotweɔn, m'enyi tua sor;
N'ayamuyie amee m', mahera No dɔm'.

. Menya Nyɛnko; O Nyɛnko bi a!
Okyii bɔgya, wui gyee me;
Nnyɛ dɛ nkwa akyɛdze ara nko,
Na mbom ɔdze Noho maa m',
Dza mowɔ nyina n' Gyefo dze a;
Musuo mu ma Ɔmafo n';
M'akoma, 'hoɔdzen, mo nkwa, ne nyina
Yɛ Nedze, Nedze afebɔɔ.

. Me ndze soɛr daa
Ye w’afamudze;
Me kra, wo so ka ho;
Kɛpem dɛ obia’ a
Bɛtse ndwom no,
Na wͻnye me atow.

. Ewuradze ma furafo hu adze; 
Osuo adwen a ɔatɔ bitsim'
Ɔma tsibowa a ɔnnda asomdwee;
Ɔboa hɔho wɔ fona mu,
Kunafo nye egyanka so
Na ɔdom daduanyi fahodzi.

. JESUS, Wo dɔ kɛse a 'wɔ ma m',
Adwen biara nnso m', gyirama nnka;
Fa me ndaase akoma fam Wo ho,
Ɔwo nkotsee na dzi do hen;
Meyɛ Wodze, Wo nkotsee dze,
Wo so yɛ me daa gyaframee.

. O mma biribiara nntsena me kra m',
Gyedɛ Wo dɔ krɔnn no nkotsee;
O ma dɔ no mfa me koraa,
Me dɛw, m'ahodze, m'ahenkyɛw;
Yi anana gyafirim fi m'akoma m',
Me nyɛe, asɛm na adwen nyɛ dɔ.

. Ao, dɔ nserɛmɛn a ema nkwagye!
Yaw nyina fi W'enyim guan koraa;
Dadwen, 'hoguan na awerɛhow kɔ,
Beebiara a W'ayarsa kan hyerɛn;
Ao Jesu! Mma munnhu hwee koraa,
Nndɔ, nnhwehwɛ hwee dɛ Wo nkotoo.

. Ma mintsiw 'yi dɛ memmberɛ,
Memper nkenya akyɛdze kɛse n';
Dɔnhwer bia 'a sakyer gyaframee
Krɔnkrɔn na sor gya 'i wɔ me kra m';
Mber nyina me dadwen nye dɛ
M'bɔbɔ akoradze krɔnkrɔn n' ho ban.

. NYAME dɔ a ɔkyɛn dɔ nyina,
Sor enyigye, sian asaase do;
Yɛ Wo tsenabea wɔ hɛn mu,
Ma W'ehumbɔbɔr nhyɛ ma;
Jesu, eyɛ mbɔbɔrhu nko,
'Yɛ dɔ mapa a 'nnyi mbanano;
Fa Wo nkwagye bɛsera hɛn,
Hɛn akoma pa biara mu.

. Me kra, tsie! Ewuradze a; 
W'Agyenkwa na ɔrekasa n';
Tsie Ne ndze; ɔreka dɛ,
Bɔnyɛnyi, ana 'dɔ M' a?

. 'Mi na megyee w' fii mpokyerɛm', 
Meyɛɛ wo pira edur;
Eyewee n', mohwehwɛɛ wo;
Memaa wo sum daan ekan.

. Adom wie n'edwuma yɛ a, 
Ibohu M'enyimnyam ntsɛm;
Enye M'bɛtsena M'ahenguam';
Bɔnyɛnyi, ana 'dɔ M' a?

. NYAME dɔ a ihuntsa; Wo krɔn,
Wo bun, dasanyi biara nnyim;
Muhu Wo kan fɛɛfɛw n' wɔ ekyir,
Mugu Wo tsenabea ho ahom;
M'akoma ridzi yaw; onnkenya
Ahotɔ, gyedɛ ɔhom Wo mu.

. Wo ndze a osuma no kɔ do frɛ m'
Dɛ monsɔ Wo kɔndua no nhwɛ;
Nkyɛ mobɔsɔ ahwɛ, naaso
Me pɛ yɛ dɛ oetsim eso okyin;
Afei ndzɛmba pii siw me kwan;
M'enyi tsim W' do, naaso mayew.

. Ɔwo dze mbɔbɔrhu aba dɛ
Memfa nhwehwɛ Wo mu asomdwee,
Na mohwehwɛ Wo a, munnhu Wo;
Me kra a orikyin nnya asomdwee;
M'ekyinkyin bɔbɔ adze dabɛn?
Nkyɛ meetutu anamɔn abɛn W'!

. Nyame nko na onyim Nyame dɔ;
O kɛtseankyɛ wɔdze aapetse
Akoma - yi mu!
Ɔdɔ ntsi misi nkrum, mepen;
Ewuradze, Wo nko yɛ m' kyɛpɛn,
Eyɛ medze a na oye.

. Kɛtseankyɛ maatsena mo Wura 
N'ananadze afebɔɔ dɛ Mary!
'Yi nye m'enyigyedze;
M'apɛdze, m'ahomka na siar,
Me dɛw, m'ahenman wɔ ase ha;
M'bɛtse Ayeforkun n' ndze.

. Ewuradze, me gyedzi gow,
M'enyidar nntum nnkyekye mo werɛ;
Mbom Wo dɔ yɛ dzen kyɛn owu;
Na modɔ Wo.

. JESU, mo Wura, me Nyankopɔn,
M'Agyenkwa, mefrɛ a tsie me;
Fi Wo tsenabea hɔ tsie me,
Wora W'adom no gu mo do;
     JESU, mo Wura, motonton Wo;
     O ma mondɔ Wo mbordo daa.

. Jesu, Ɔwo bɛyɛ mo ndwom;
M'akoma na me kra Wodze a;
Dza mowɔ na meyɛ Wodze a,
Ɔwo Gyefo Siarfo, yɛ medze.

. Wimu abɔdze nyina yɛ komm 
Twa hɛn asaase ho hyia dɛn, 
Ndze anaa dede bi nnyi hɔ a, 
Obi wɔ hɔn mu a ɔtse;
Wodzi dɛw wɔ dza ɔfata ho,
Na wɔdze enyimnyam ndze paa m' ka;
Ber a wɔhyerɛn n', wɔtow ndwom daa;
Nsa a ɔyɛɛ hɛn no yɛ krɔnkrɔn!

. Yɛtse ase, kɔ ba a,
Na N'adom ara ntsi a;
Ɔda ho hwɛ ɔkra biara a
Ɔtse ase, kɔ na ɔba;
Na ɔdze hɛn nkwa ma hɛn bio
Ɔdze ma hɛn aber biara.

. Ɔdɔ na opia hɛn anamɔn
Enyigye ahorɛadze m';
Mbɔnsam nyim na hɔn ho popo;
Mbom Satan dze onnyi dɔ.

. Megyee enyim tɔɔ gon sum mu,
Mohwehwɛɛ Wo na mifii nkyɛn;
M'adwen kyinii kɔr ekyirkyir,
Modɔɔ W'abɔdze kyɛɛn Ɔwo;
Seseiara muhu biribi,
Wo kan mu na iyi fa ba.

. Ewia a wɔammbɔ W', meda W'ase
Dɛ Wo kan nserɛmɛn hyerɛn mo do;
Meda Wo ase dɛ aka
M'atamfo egu, asa m'adwen yar;
Meda Wo ase dɛ Wo ndze
Ma m'akoma nya fahodzi.

. Ma m'enyiwa ntaataa nyinsu,
Ma gya krɔnkrɔn mfram m'akoma;
Fa Egya ho suro ma me kra,
Ɔdɔ a ɔhyɛ sor dɔm nyina nkuran;
Ama meetum nye hɔn nyina
Abɔ m' kor ahyɛ W' enyimnyam.

. M'bɔdɔ W', m'enyigye, m'ahenkyɛw,
M'bɔdɔ Wo, mo Wura, me Nyame;
Wo bo fuw me mpo a, m'bɔdɔ Wo
Eyerɛw W'ano anaa Wo poma o;
Kaansa mo honam yi prɔw mpo a,
M'bɔdɔ Wo akɔ onnyiewiei m'.

. Dɛw a enam yaw mu hwehwɛ me n',
Murunntum mmfa m'akoma nnsuma Wo;
Menam nsu m' hwehwɛ nyankontɔn,
Minyim dɛ anohoba n' nnyɛ gyan;
'Su bɔbɔ adze anapa.

. M-bowadoma nyina
Enyi gye kwaamu;
Ndua atsentsen do
Na nnoma gyinagyina;
Wɔdze hɔn ndwom dɛɛdɛw
Hyɛ kwaa no mu ma;
Hɔn mberɛbuw wɔ mban mu
Dze tweɔn esusowber.

. Mepɛ meehu na maatahye
No dɔ krɔnkrɔn n' no bun, no krɔn,
Ayamuyie a edze ayɛ me,
Emi a wɔdze mo bɔn soaa Wo;
Emi ntsi na me Nyame wui;
Owui dze gyee me kra fii 'wu m'.

. O M'AGYENKWA, tsie me,
Twe me fam Wo ho;
Ɔwo etua me kaw nyina,
Ɔwo ewu ama m';
Afei medze gyedzi gye
Adom fi W'adom dzin mu;
Ɔwo nye m' Guandɔbea,
Ma m' nguan mbra Wo hɔ.

. O m'Agyenkwa, hyira me,
Fa me yɛ Wodze;
Mma nngyaa m' ma minnkyinkyin
Wɔ wiadze yi mu;
Fa Wo kan hyerɛn mo kwan mu,
Ma W'enyimnyam nhyerɛn mo ho;
Mo Botan, Guandɔbea,
Fa me yɛ Wodze.

. O m'Agyenkwa, kora me,
Kora me daa nyina;
Hyira m', dɔ me, kyerɛ m'kwan
Kɛpem m'edwuma asa;
Na afei medze enyigye
Bɔtow W'ayɛyi wɔ sor;
Hɔ menye m'Agyenkwa
Bɛtsena Afebɔɔ.

. MOFONAA pii, mennya wiadze ahomgye;
Mikyinkyiin pii, mennya ahomgyebea;
Ekyir yi, minyaa no wɔ No bo mu,
Nyia obue Ne nsa ma bahatɔfo;
No mu na minyaa fie ahomgyebea;
Ofi hɔ n'meyɛ Nedze, na ɔyɛ m'dze.

. Papa biara a mowɔ fir Noara;
Me haw no onyim dɛ oye ma me;
Me Nyɛnko nye No a, meyɛ sikafo;
Mowɔ adze nyina na ɔnnka m' ho a, midzi hia;
Nsakyer ba a, mepen do, anaa mopow,
Meyɛ Nedze, na ɔyɛ m'dze a mo bo dwe.

. Nsesa biara ba a, Ɔno ɔnnsesa;
Ewia nyimnyamfo a n'ano nntɔ mu da;
Ɔnantsew fua na ehum do wɔ wimu,
Na ɔhyerɛn No nkorɔfo do sum mu;
Sɛ hɔn nyina kɔ mpo a, munnsuro da,
Ber a Gyefo n' yɛ medze, meyɛ Nedze.

. Ha yi muhu No dɔ kumabaa bi,
Muhu No kakra, tonton No kakra;
Na sɛ muhu No wɔ sor man mu hɔ a,
Mobɔdɔ No yie, na masom No yie;
Na m'bɛka N'adwontofo krɔnkrɔn ho,
M'bedzi mu mayɛ Nedze, ɔayɛ m'dze.

. ONYIMPA Ba, Wo bo mu
Yɛ guandɔbea ma me,
Yɛ mo sumabea ahomgye,
'Siandɛ ehum no so;
Gye m' fi ehum dzendzen nsa;
Yɛ m'akatado wɔ ehum mu;
Jesus, fa me sie na ma
Bɔn ehum no mbɛsen.

. Motwe moho fi wiadze a
Dede na bɔn ahyɛ m' n' ho;
Medze ahopopo tweɔn
Wo ndze a ɔyɛ berɛww no;
Mayɛ komm wɔ W'enyim koraa
Mennsɛ dɛ mutu ntsen mpo;
Yi Wo dɔ a osuma n' kyerɛ
Me kra a ɔrotweɔn no.

. Ewuradze, me mber wɔ W' nsamu,
Dan me kra bra Wo hɔ;
Kaansa meyɛ nyaa akoma m' a,
Ɔwo bɛma m' ntseasee;
Wo mu na metse, kɔ ba,
Ndwuma, ayɛyi nyina Wodze a,
Eyɛ nyansa, tum na dɔ;
Mbrɛ etse nyina medze a.  Amen.

. Dɛm mber no yɛ mber fɛɛfɛw a ɔnntɔ ka;
Tsena mo mu na ɔbɛtsena hɔ afebɔɔ;
Ma Wo nhyehyɛɛ nye me mpaabɔ mbra mu;
Bra bɛtsena mo mu, na mentsena Wo mu.  Amen.

. Bra, bɔsoɛ me! Mebue abow n' sesei; 
Mo Wura, minyim Wo ndze, dɛ Ɔwoara a.
Ewia atɔ dada na ehum reba;
Me Gyefo, ayɛ mbrɛ ebɔsoɛ me, bra!

. Mo kɔn dɔ ɔsor nkwa nsu n',
Na ha daa nyina ɔpem;
Mohwehwɛ W' dɔ n'egyapadze n'
Na onnyi ekyir koraa;
Ndwom fofor wɔ m'anomu a
Wɔahyehyɛ n' ɔdɔ ndwom;
W'adom nyina ntsi enyimnyam
Nka Wo; minnyaa nnkaa nnhwɛe.

. O me Gyefo, gyina me nkyɛn 
Wɔ nsɔhwɛ dzendzen ber m';
Fa Wo nsa a atsen mu n' gye m',
Na kyerɛ Wo tum nyina;
O dwen W'asɔm no ho na
Hue W'adom mapa n' gu mo do;
Domfo Ewuradze, kora me,
Na mma nngyaa m' mma monnkɔ!

. Mma mimmfi Wo bom' ara da
Monntɔ dɔnsuar, Gyefo;
Ɔwo nye m' Boafo na Ahom,
Nokwar, asetsena Kwan n';
M'akatua abɔso mapa,
Wɔ heaven na asaase do ha;
Domfo Ewuardze, kora me,
Na mma nngya m' mma monnkɔ!  Amen.

. Jesus, n-kyɛ 'nye m' aanantsew 
Na meefi honam akwan do;
'Wo nye mo Kwan, yɛ m' Kwankyerɛfo;
Fa me nan si botan no do.

. 'KRA bahatɔfo, yɛ dzen,
Tweɔn W'Ewuradze Ne ber pa;
Kaansa N'asɛm kyɛr dɛn ara a,
Ɔyɛ nokwar na osi pi;
Medze me kra twer N'asɛm,
Onnkotwa abrɔdɔ da;
Asɛm n' bɛba m' ampaara
Orunntwa abrɔdɔ ara da.

. Ewuradze, me mber wɔ W' nsamu;
Matɔ bahaw, yɛ mberɛw mpo a,
Ɔwo bɛma meegyina pirim;
'Mi megye Jesus dzin n' dzi,
Nsɔhwɛ mu Gyefo nye Wo,
Agye me nkwa dadaada;
Egye m' nkwa fi bɔn m' sesei,
Ebɔkɔ do ara agye m'.

. Wo pɛrpɛr gyina hɔ pintsinn
Dɛ mbepɔw a hɔn fapem etsim;
Wo nsaano edwuma yɛ nwanwa;
W'atsɛmbu dɔ dɛ po no bun.

. Jesus dzin nwanwa no
Ma hɛn atamfo nyina guan;
Jesus brɛfo, 'Guambaa dzendzen,
Ɔyɛ Gyata wɔ ɔko m',
Yɛnye hɛll dɔm dzi esi;
Yetu hɛll dɔm nyina gu;
Yedzi hɔn do Jesu bɔgyaa m',
Yebedzi konyim daa.

. Hɛn Sahen dzi hɛn kan;
Ɔto hɛn nsa fi sor,
Na ɔdze ahenkyɛw hyɛnn kyerɛ hɛn,
Ɔdɛ yɛngye akatua n';
Ndzi nokwar nkodu owu m',
Hom nye M' nkyɛ Mo konyim;
Na hom bɔbɔ enyimnyam abɔtsir n'
Na hom nye M' edzi hen!

. TSIE! Ɔweɔmfo n' ndze nye n';
'Nuanom, hom nyan!
Jesus Noara ɔabɛn;
Nuanom, hom nyan!
Sum mu mba na wɔda!
Homdze, hom yɛ kan mu mba;
'Nyimnyam hyɛnn n' yɛ homdze;
Nuanom, hom nyan!

. Hom nse hɔn a wonyan dɛ;
'Nuanom, hom nweɔn!
Hɛn Wura N'asɛm pefee;
'Nuanom, hom nweɔn!
Hom nyɛ dɛ mbanyin a daa
Wɔtweɔn hɔn Wura N'abowano;
Kaansa ɔyɛ ekyim mpo a,
Nuanom, hom nweɔn!

. Yentsie hɛn Wura Ne frɛ;
Hom nyɛ edwuma!
Obia a benya bi ayɛ,
Hom nyɛ edwuma!
Edwuma wɔ Ewuradze
No wenyin turo m' dabaa;
Ɔbɛma hom akatua;
Hom nyɛ edwuma!

. ATAMFO etwa moho ehyia,
Fie atamfo abɔ mo ho aprɔw,
Munntum mmfi nsa, munntum nngyina enyim;
Mo nko nye hɛll, bɔn na asaase,
Mo nko ara naaso munnsuro;
Megye Jesu dzin midzi pi.

. Dɔm mpempem ba mo do ntsi dɛn?
Wiadze pusow me kra ntsi dɛn?
Mowɔ akokyɛm a ɔbɔbɔ hɔn egu;
Obepia akofo n' akɔ ekyir;
Wohu Eguambaa bɔgyaa wɔ m' mu;
Megye Jesu dzin midzi pi.

. N-kwagye wɔ Ne dzin m' papa,
N-kwagye fi bɔn, 'wu na hɛll,
N-kwagye a wɔdze kɔ dɛw mu;
N- kwagye kɛse a, wɔka n' dɛw?
Na megye dza ɔwɔ ma m' nyina;
Megye Jesu dzin midzi pi.   Amen.

. Dɛ mbrɛ tsetse n' iyii Woho n'; 
Kyerɛw krɔnkrɔn bɔ Wo dzin dawur;
Ɔwo a ennsakyer ara da,
Fa W'ahentum kɛse n' bɛn hɛn.

. Ahotɔ enyidar yɛ siar koraa!
Ɔma akra a wɔatɔ bitsi do;
Ɔdze ewufo ba nkwa m';
Hɛn aperdzi ha bɔbɔ adze ntsɛm,
Na nkyii emi na ɔwo nye hɛn Hen
Bosoɛr konyimdzi mu.

. Hom mma hom akoma ndzi dɛw;
Hom mfa sor akodze nhyɛ nko;
Mma hom nndwen dɛ ɔko n' war;
Hom bɔtow konyim ndwom ntsɛm.

. 'Siandɛ Nyame kyɛn mbrɛ yɛdwen;
N'akwan bor hɛn nyimdzee;
Ɔbor hɛn ntseasee, na wɔdze
Mbofra dɔ du Ne nkyɛn.

. Etweɔn dɛ 'bɔkɔ do adom hɛn;
Etse abɔnfo ase;
Hɛn ɔgye m', yehu W'ayamuyie,
Yɛaka W'adom nyina.

. FA W'ahom nyina ko ɔko pa n';
Christ yɛ w'ahoɔdzen na wo tum;
Suo nkwa mu yie na ɔbɛyɛ
W'enyigye ahenkyɛw afebɔɔ.

. Dua Nyame N'adom do tu enguan n';
To w'enyi wimu hwɛ N'enyim,
N-kwa na ɔda w'enyim yi;
Christ yɛ ɔkwan na akatua.

. Etumfo nye akɛsefo 
Rotwe hɔn dɔm wɔ akono,
Wɔbɔkɔ wo ntoa awerɛfirm';
 	Weɔn na sɔr.
 
. Fa wo sor akodze n' mia; 
Ma ɔnhyɛ wo daa nyina;
Ɔtamfo n' rehyɛ w' atsɛw:
                    Weɔn na sɔr.

. 'DƆ mu ɔdɔ, na kan mu Kan,
Ɔsor Egya a ehwɛ ne nyina;
Nyansa a wɔdze esuma sorsor,
Bɔadze, ɔwo na ayɛ no dɛm;
Bɔfo nwanwanyi, pɛrpɛr m'
Afrɛ m'akoma dɛ ɔntwer Wo.

. NYIA ɔtwer Nyame
Nokwafo no,
Oesi ne dan no petsee;
Nyia ɔdze n' ho to
Jesus Christ do n',
Heaven bɛyɛ n'adze pa;
Medze mo werɛ
Behyɛ Wo mu
'Siandɛ Wo nokwar n' nnsakyer;
Ber a 'yɛ medze 'i;
'Wu n' hu biara
Rennsakyer m'akokodur.

. 'Kra nokwafo, bɔ mpaa daa
Kɔ do ara twer Nyame;
Ɔbɛma w'anamɔn etsim,
Ɔronnhwɛ mma mmpatser;
Twer Wo Pomfo No bom' daa,
Ɔno ɔkora wo sunsum,
Mese w', hom wɔ No mu sɔnn;
Wo weɔmfo n' nnda ara da.

. Bɔn anaa asaase nye hɛll 
Rinndzi Wo weɔmfo do;
N-komtɔ gyangyan biara
Nnkowia N'enyiwa pɛnn n';
Ɔbɔ Israel ho ban pa;
Israel bɛkyerɛ N' hwɛdo pa n',
Ber a ɔweɔn hɔn daa yi;
Na No dɔ mmbɔ adze.

. ME kra nam n'ahohia na awerɛhow m' botu
Akɔ Botan a ɔkrɔn kyɛn me n' hɔ sɔnn;
Bɔnyɛnyi a meyɛ mberɛw, m'bɛyɛ Wodze daa;
Ɔwo siar Tsetse Bo, musuma Wo mu!
   Musuma Wo mu! Musuma Wo mu daa!
   Ɔwo siar Tsetse Bo, Musuma Wo mu!

. M'AKOMA, taa dzinn! Nyame dze nye m';
Ɔyɛɛ m' nyimpa, otu mo suro,
Ewuradze abɔ me dzinn afrɛ m';
Otwitwa gye m', ɔbɛn me daa;
No bɔgyaa bɔɔ m' werdam prɛko,
Na ɔda ho dɔ m' na ɔweɔn me.

. Ber a menam nsubun mu no,
Mudua gyedzi m' bisa No mboa;
Asorɛkye n' bɔ kɔ kan ara yie,
Na ɔadwe fɛmm wɔ me tsir do;
Munnsuro ne begyabegyayɛ;
Nyame wɔ hɔ 'i ɔnnkɛhaw me.

. Moto gyedzi enyiwa hwɛ No,
Menam 'gya m' ara kɔ m'enyim;
Ogya n' werɛ fir dɛ ɔbɛdzɛw,
Gyaframee no dzi mo ho agor;
Mowɔ No tum n' gyedɛ ahyɛnsew n',
Medze nkekam' fa ma me Gyefo n'.

. O me Gyefo, gyina me nkyɛn daa!
Na weɔn me nsɔhwɛ dzendzen mu;
Fa me sie Wo nsa donkonn mu,
Kyerɛ Wo nkwagye tum wɔ mo do;
W'abasa ntwitwa ngye me daa,
'Saase nye hɛll nnkotum atsew m'.

. ABƆDZE nyina Tumfo, m'Agyenkwa Hen,
Fa Wo tsenenee bra na bɔboa hɛn;
W'anohoba hyɛ W' dɛ nya ayamuhyehye;
Ma munhu dɛ 'wɔ tum a ɔgye nkwa sesei.

. Dɔnhwer biara migyina esian mu;
Edze me nsamu ntsi mowɔ ahoɔdzen;
Ber a mugu do refrɛ 'i, metse Wo mboa nka;
Ɔgye m' fi asehwe m' anaa ohwim me fi hɛll.

. Nyame krɔn sen nyimpa, abɔnsam nye bɔn;
Me Jesus dɔ bedzi konyim ɔko n' mu;
Ne mbae bɛyɛ enyimnaym kɛse a ɔyɛ hu,
No dɔ mapa n' bedzi konyim ama me.

. MA Nyame nhwɛ W'akwan nyina,
Nya No m' enyidado ber nyina;
Da bɔn mu n 'bohu No dɛ
W'ahoɔdzen nye Kwankyerɛfo;
Nyia ɔtwer Nyame dɔ a ɔnnsakyer n'
Si dan wɔ botan a otsim hɔ do.

. Tow ndwom yɛ asɔr, mmfi N'akwan ho,
Yɛ w'afamudze nokwar mu ara;
Twer No bɔhyɛ a adom ahyɛ n' ma n',
Dɛm na obesi wo yie ama w';
Nyame mmbu N'enyi nngu ɔkra a
Ɔtwer N' mapa n' n'ehiadze do.

. Tow wo suro nyina kyen;
Nya enyidar, w'abaw nngura;
Nyame tse w' nkrumsi nye wo su,
Ɔbɛma w' tsir do sor.

. Mberɛwyɛnyi mepaa Wo mprɛnsa,
'Nyaa W'enyim mbɔbɔrhu;
Nyia ɔsakyeer asɛndua do n'
Wɔdze n' kɔr Paradise,
Bɔn nye ahohia dɔnhwer mu n',
Christ, ma yenhu W'enyim;
Nnuho mu a aka hɛn nko n';
Jesus, ma hɛn adom.

. Enyidado mprɛnsa,
Ma me akomatɔm';
M'Egya Ne nsa siesie kuraba n';
Nye dza onyim dɛ oye.

. FI mo do, ekyingye, m'Agyenkwa bɛn me,
Na m'ahotɔ ntsi ɔbɛba abɛgye m';
Me nam mpaabɔ mu meper na ɔbɛyɛ;
Menye Christ wɔ hɛn mu, meserew ehum.

. 'Sinadɛ dza mihia nyina ye ma m' ntsi
Dza ɔyɛ wen yɛ dɛw, edur yɛ edziban;
Sesei dze ɔyɛ yaw, ɔnnkɛkyɛr na egyaa;
Dɛm ber n' o, konyimdzifo ndwom bɛyɛ dɛw!

. Kwan m' yɛ tɔɔtsen, a motow ndwom,
Kwan mu yɛ hu a, mobɔ mpaa;
Sɛ mbusu mu a, sufrɛ No;
Motwer Jesus, noara nye n'.

. W'abaw mu na mohom;
Atamfo a wɔhaw me
Nsa rennka me ha;
Asaase wosow mpo a,
Nyimpa nyina akoma tu a,
Jesus bɔ m' suro ham;
Bɔn nye hɛll nyina hwe ase,
Ehum dzendzen bunkam mo do a,
Jesus nnkɛpa me da.

. Meda W' ase dɛ edze dza oye
Esie ama hɛn;
Yɛwɔ pii naaso ɔnndɔɔ so,
Yɛnnhwehwɛ bio;
Hɛn kɔn dɔ asomdwee mapa a
Ne saso nnka.

. HƐN Agyenkwa Nyame dɔ ntsi
Ɔbɛyɛ yie;
N'adom a ɔdze ma kwa, ɔnnsakyer,
Ne nyina ye;
N'adehye bɔgya sa hɛn yar;
N'adom kɛse sɔw hɛn ano;
Ne nsa a ɔwowaw hɛn n' yɛ dzen,
Ɔbɛyɛ yie.

. Kaansa yɛnam ɔhaw mu mpo a,
Ɔbɛyɛ yie;
Christ atɔ hɛn nkwagye ewie,
Ne nyina ye;
Yedzi dɛw wɔ hɛn nkwagye ewie,
Yɛtse Christ mu a yɛsow aba,
Yɛyɛ krɔnkrɔn wɔ Sunsum mu;
Ɔbɛyɛ yie.

. Ma mentse nka dɛ ebɛn me,
Wiadze bɛn me dabaa;
Muhu dza osiw enyiwa do,
Metse engyigye so nka;
M'atamfo bɛn me dabaa,
Wɔabɔ mo ho aprɔw;
Mbom Jesus, twe bɛn me, na
Gye me kra fi bɔn mu.

. Ndzɛmba nyina rutwa m'akɔ;
Nyimpa sɛe na mber twa mu;
Naaso N'adom do nnhuan da koraa;
Nyam' nye nyansa, Nyam' nye dɔ.

. WIADZE Kan, mihyira Wo nserɛmɛn n';
Tsenenee Ewia, Wo nko do na
Me gyedzi enyi tsim;
Igya me 'i, mudua ne nyina m',
Munnsuro mbusu biara wɔ ha,
'Siandɛ ebɛn me da.

. Samanadze etumfo runntum mmpuw
Ɔkra a ɔnye Christ nam kan mu;
Ɔnantsew, ɔnnhwe ase;
Ohu adze kann, tsin no kwan do,
Ɔwɔw do hyerɛn kodu da pa n',
Odzi adze nyina do nyim.

. Mohom Wo tum kɛse n' ase;
Jesus Ne dzin yɛ abantsentsen,
Ɔkora me kra wɔ sor;
Onnkegyaa dɛ ɔyɛ mo Boafo;
Mo werɛ nyina hyɛ Wo mu,
Dɔ Nyame nokwafo.

. Mpaabɔ yɛ Christian n'ahom pa,
Christian man no mu mfar,
Tum a ɔdze hɛn owu abotsen m';
Ɔdze mpaabɔ hɛn sor;

. Dua Wo ntotɔserɛ Sunsum n' do
Bra hɛn a yɛrotweɔn Wo mbae n' nkyɛn;
Yɛserɛ W'akyɛdze n' mu kor pɛr,
Tum a wɔdze sɔr aber biara;
Yeewura, dom hɛn ebisadze yi,
Na mma mmfa nkaa no so nnkam hɛn.

. Inu m'ahoɔdzen mu fofor;
Na edze mo bɔn nyina kyɛ m';
Na edze sor enyidar kyekye
Ankonam werɛ.

. Kasa bi nntum nnkyerɛ siar ahomka n',
Hɔ minya m'ebisadze nyina;
Ɔko mu ahoɔdzen, yaw mu edur;
Asomdwee bɛn a!

. Ekyingye bɔm, suro nyina tu;
Mo sunsum pɛ akɔtsena sor;
Na m'awerɛhow mu nyinsuwakyi
So mpo pepa.

. Inu m'ahoɔdzen mu fofor;
Na edze mo bɔn nyina kyɛ m';
Na edze sor enyidar kyekye
Ankonam werɛ.

. Kasa bi nntum nnkyerɛ siar ahomka n',
Hɔ minya m'ebisadze nyina;
Ɔko mu ahoɔdzen, yaw mu edur;
Asomdwee bɛn a!

. Ekyingye bɔm, suro nyina tu;
Mo sunsum pɛ akɔtsena sor;
Na m'awerɛhow mu nyinsuwakyi
So mpo pepa.

. Ereba Ɔhen enyim;
Fa w'ebisadze nyina bra;
N'adom nye No tum dɔɔ so,
Ebisadze biara nnso.

. Medze m'adzesoa hyɛ ase;
Ewuradze, yi mo bɔn yi;
Ma Wo bɔgyaa a 'huee maa abɔn n'
Mpon me tsibowa mfi bɔn mu.

. Ewuradze, mepɛ ahomgye;
Fa m'akoma ndɔmmum nwionn;
Ma ɔnye Wo bɔgyaa atɔdze,
Wo nkotoo na dzi mu hen.

. BƆ mpaa, kɔ do ara,
Wo Sahen na ɔka yi;
Fa enyigye yɛ setsie ma No,
Na su frɛ W'Ewuradze;
Fa w'ehiadze brɛ No,
Bɔ mpaa ka kyerɛ Nyame;
Bɔ mpaa daa;mma mmpa abaw da;
Bɔ mpaa, kɔ do ara!

. O Ewuradze, nye me nkɔ!
'Nye me ntsena amma meennguan;
W'asɛm nhyɛ m' dzen wɔ mo mu;
Minya awerɛkyekyer mo mu;
Suo me nsamu ma munhu Wo,
Yɛ m' nokwafo kodu ewiei.  Amen.

. Adze nyinaa ne yɛ nnyɛ dzen mma  
Nyia otum gye Jesu dzin dzi;
Munngu Wo nokwar n' ho fi bio,
Mo Wura, megye n' dɔ mu ara;
Mutum, megye Wo dzi ampa,
Adze nyinaa ne yɛ nnyɛ dzen mma m'.

. Dza ɔyɛ dzen sen adze nyina 
Nye dɛ m'begyaa bɔn yɛ koraa;
Naaso ne yɛ nnyɛ dzen, minyim:
Jesus, hwɛ Wo nokwaredzi no!
Sɛ biribiara nnyɛ dzen mma Wo a,
Adze nyina ne yɛ nnyɛ dzen mma m'
 
. Asaase nye hɛll gye kyim mpo a, 
Nyame N'asɛm nnkotwa apaw da;
Eguambaa n' beyi mo bɔn koraa,
Ampa, sɛ ɔyɛ dzen mpo a;
Dza ɔyɛ dzen mpo ɔbɛyɛ;
Adze nyina ne yɛ nnyɛ dzen mma m'.

. Mbersantsen Panyin, yɛtse W’ mu;
Wo mfesantsen mu na yenya
Hɛn asomdwee na dɛw;
Yɛhom wͻ hɛn daa Nyame mu,
Yɛtsena dwudwoodwɔ, asomdweem’,
Wͻ Ͻwo a ennsakyer da m’.

. Yɛgya sum na suro wͻ ekyir,
Yenya kan fofor na enyimnyam,
Yenya ahenman fofor;
‘Dze adom awoo na mpuei fofor ba;
Yɛtow konyimdzi ndwom fofor
Hyira Foforyɛnyi n’.

. Yɛsoɛr na yɛhom wͻ Wo mu,
Yɛtsena fie, yepue  kͻhwehwɛ;
Yɛda ho tse Wo mu.
Dɛw na ahodwuruw yɛ kɛse;
Ͻma yenya nkwa fofor fi
Nyame a ennsakyer da hͻ.

. SƐ yɛdze hɛn dadwen to W' do a;
Ewuradze, nkyɛ yebedzi dɛw;
Sɛ yɛsakyer hɛn su a,
Yɛtse hɛn akoma m' dɛ Obi wɔ sor,
Ɔyɛ nyansabuakwa nye ɔdɔ,
Ɔreyɛ edwuma pa.

. Membrɛ moho adze ngye nkyérɛkyérɛ;
O ma menyɛ abofra a ͻdwe,
Ntsiatsia mo Wfira n’anamon mu!
Mma me kra nnhu W’ebufuwhyew,
'Nyitan, ’nyiber, nyinkuntwe nkͻ;
Ͻdo m’ na yɛ ndzɛmba fofor.

. Na Woara hye m‘apɛdze do;
Munhu kan a ͻwͻ Wo kan mu.
Memfa enyimtsewee nhwɛ Wo;
Wͻafrɛ m' dɛ menkyérɛ W‘ gyedzi tum,
Ma m’akoma a ho tsew nyɛ ͻdͻ,
Me bra a fi nnyi ho nyɛ ayɛyi.  Amen.

. Wo nkwa a ͻsom bo a dze mae no
Kyérɛ adorn n’ase wͻ mo mu;
Yi me fi emumuyɛ nyina m’;
Ma me dzibew. memfata sor:
Gyedɛ tsew mo ho fi nyina m’,
Wo yaw nye me gyedzi yɛ kwa.

. Wo nokwar nye mbͻbͻrhu ntsi
Gye W'akowaa yɛ Woara Wodze;
Tsew W'enyimnyam dzin ho mo mu;
Fa m' yɛ Wo nko Wodze ndɛ ara,
Sesa m' na ma mo ho ntsew koraa;
Mentsena ase, nwu mma Wo nko.  Amen.

. Hohor mo bɔn biara fi hɔ;
Totow m'ehonyi nyinara gu;
Tsew mo ho fi adwembɔn biara m',
Fi efifidze na ahopɔw m'.

. Wo dzin ama menya Wo su;
Iyi nko dze, fa ma m';
Memmpɛ hwee dɛ me Nyankopɔn,
Wɔ asaase do anaa sor.

. MENYA Ɔba n' nsamu fahodzi 'i,
Ma monsɔ m' fahodzi nhwɛ;
Memfa m'enyiwa nhwɛ Wo,
Ndzi nyim wɔ nkwa adom mu;
Mfa enyigye nkyerɛ Wo pɛ n',
Enyimnyam wɔ dɔ mapa m'.

. Abba, Egya, tsie Wo ba,
Ka me bɔ m' wɔ Jesus mu;
Tsie na petse adom nhyira n',
Wɔ dɛw, asomdwee nye tum m';
M'Agyenkwa, serɛ wɔ sor ma m',
Nkwa na sor dɔ nyinara.

. Ɔsor Adam, ɔsor Nkwa,
Dan mo su ma ɔnsɛ Wodze;
Hɛn me kra nyinara mu,
Hyɛ no dzen na hyɛ no ma;
Ɔnyɛ dɛ menntse honam m'
Na mbom mentse Wo mu.

. Sunsum Krɔnkrɔn, mma nnyɛ ekyim;
Bra bɛtsena W'asɔrfi mu;
Dzi dase mo sunsum mu,
Ɔnyɛ dzen na ontsim hɔ;
N-kwa nsunyiwa, hue ma m',
Tsena m'akoma m' afebɔɔ. Amen.

. Nyimdzee nwanwa a ɔdɔ, ɔkrɔn;
Hen na abɔdze bosuma?
Meda W'abaw a atserɛw mu do;
Etwa mo ho ehyia.

. NYAME, sor na asaase Wura,
Ebɛn afɔr na mombɔ mma W'?
Mo sunsum, kra na honam, gye
Nyikan afɔrbɔ krɔnkrɔn no;
Osuar dze, m'adze nyina nye n';
Mowɔ n' pii a, nkyɛ medze bɛma W'.

. Afei, Nyame, me kra yɛ W'dze,
Ɔnnyɛ m'dze bio, meyɛ Wodze;
Weɔn Woara W'dze, yɛ n' Wodze nwionn,
Ma enyidado na dɔ mfram;
Gye mo sunsum, ma W'enyimnyam
Nhyerɛn mu nkɛpem da a m'bedzi mu.

. W'asɔrfi krɔnn n' atsew mo ho,
Etu esi hɔ ama Wo pɛ;
Ma Wo kan nhyerɛn daa wɔ ha,
Bra bɛhyɛ fie ha daa nyina;
Nkwa Mafo, tsena mo mu, nunu m'
Kɛpem dɛ dɔ bɛhyɛ me ma.

. Dɛ wodze W' dzin kɛse n' frɛ me 'i,
Fa W' Sunsum hoɔdzenfo n' kora me;
Mo nsusui nyina mbɔ m' wɔ mo mu,
Mo ndwuma nyina mu n' yɛ mo botae;
Wo dɔ no ngya m' me mber nyina,
M'edwuma nye dɛ m'beyi W' ayew.

. Gye me kra na nyimpadua;
Gye m'adwendwen na me pɛ,
Me ndzɛmba na me mber nyina;
Dza minyim, metse nka nyina,
Dza modwen, meka, meyɛ;
Gye m'akoma na yɛ n' fofor.

. Ne nsamu aprandaa
Ma wiadze nyina bɔ hu;
N'ebufuw na tsenenee
Weɔn Ne mbra krɔnkrɔn no;
Na mbrɛ No dɔ pɛ dɛ ohyira n'.
No nokwar si adom no pi.

. Nyansa nwanwa hyerɛn 
No ndwuma akɛse mu; 
Ɔsɛɛ hɛll etumfo
Na hɔn sum ndwuma nyina; 
Ne basa dzen ma Ne nhyehyɛɛ 
Na N'apɛdze nyina yɛ hɔ.

. Ndwuma nyina ye, biara ye koraa,
Sɛ ɔsɔ W'enyi dze a;
Dwumayɛnyi biara a ɔdze dɔ som
Ne mfɛfo n' sɔ W'enyi;
Ennhyira amma nyimpa na dwuma
Biara ho kwan a, onngyina.

. Hɛn Wura, dwuma biara a edzi n',
'Pɛ dɛ hɛn so yɛyɛ;
Yɛnye N' yɛ edwuma, ama obiara so 
Nye N' aakyɛ N'abayɛ n';
Ewuradze, mbɔsom, maayɛ ba;
Meserɛ W', mma nnyi m' tokyen.

. Nyame asomfo, hom nsoɛr! 
Asɔr no rotweɔn hom;
N'edwuma so ma n'hoɔdzen;
Hom nsoɛr, hom nhyɛ no dzen.

. TWEƆN, Owura, tweɔn wɔ kokwaa yi do ha;
Tsintsim na nye hɛn ntsena ha kakra;
Yɛnye tsetsemba akatakyi nyina
Bɛtsena Nyame bea nwanwa yi do;
Begyina ahopopo m' wɔ kan ahengua enyim,
Abɔ nkɔtsen ahwɛ sunsum wiadze n'.

. Tweɔn, Owura, tweɔn! Yɛgye mfar pa wɔ ha;
Nnyɛ asetsena a ɔrotweɔn hɛn hɔ n' nye yi;
Adwen, atsenka, nyina dzi akɔnaaba;
Yennkotum aka ho asɛm, yennyim koraa;
Awɔw na kan kyekyer hɛn ma yɛhwɛ
Abɔ nkɔtsen ahwɛ sunsum wiadze n'.

. Ewuradze se, Dabi, ber apa ho;
Yɛnkɔ hɛn fie, 'bra na edwuma wɔ ase,
Yebu ntwɛr wɔ mpaabɔ koko do ha n',
Edwumadze wɔ ase hɔ rotweɔn hɛn,
Ha 'i yɛhwehwɛ Nyame ma yeehu N' pɛ;
Hɔ yɛyɛ N' pɛ, som No, hwehwɛ N' ara.

. Sɛ nyimpa per du Nyame ahengua n' ho a,
Kwan n' da asaase kusuww yi do ha ara;
Nyia ɔyɛ ne famu ha edwuma dɛ mbrɛ ɔsɛ n',
Wɔbɔkrɔn n' kɛse wɔ sor ahenman m';
Hɛn akra hwehwɛ ahom Nyame N'ananadze,
Na nyi ɔsom No yie n' bɛn No kɛse.

. Yɛ edwuma; hwer, ma woho nkɔm', 
Fa dɛw yɛ w'Egya N'edwuma;
Kwan a wo Wura duaa mu nye n';
Na 'wo, somfo, na ennkɛfa do?

. Yɛ ara, eso dzi mu dɛw; 
Na ahomgye pa wɔ ekyir;
Ɔrennkyɛr bi na atse kumfor n'
Ne ndze esuom dɛ, Hwɛ, mereba!

. M'ENYI daa kwan dɛ mibenya
Kyɛfa wɔ 'hoɔdzenfo m';
Medze botae a ho tsew, ɔkrɔn
Bɔfora mbɔdzembɔfo m';
Nyame ahyehyɛ kwan kor so,
Na ɔahyehyɛ no yie;
Medze yaw akoma kaa dɛm
Ber a dɛm ɔhaw yɛ bae.

. M'akoma yɛ mberɛw,
Kɛpem dɛ obohu n' Wura;
Ɔnnyi ndzeyɛɛ pa ho awerɛhyɛm';
Ɔnye mframa sesa,
Onnyi ne fahodzi,
Gyedɛ atsew no mpokyerɛ m';
Yɛ n' akowaa wɔ Wo dɔ a ɔnnsa n' mu,
Na obedzi hen wɔ nkwa m'.

. Mo tum yɛ har, yɛ mberɛw,
Kɛpem dɛ mesua som;
Ɔhwehwɛ dɛ onya gya a ɔdzɛw,
Ɔpɛ mframa a ɔma ahom;
Onntum nndzi wiadze enyim,
Gyedɛ wɔdze n' bodu;
Wobotum ehim ne frankaa n'
Ber a ebɔhom efi sor.

. Mma nnhwehwɛ asaase pa
Wɔ ha anaa noho;
Wohu no nkokwaa na mbɔnsa m';
Kɔ do gu n' beebiara.

. Mbrɛ ɔtse biara obefir;
Ahoɔfɛw na ahoɔdzen m';
Ɔbɔwowɔ, oenyin afa mba,
Na afei ɔayɛ eburow-mu.

. HƆN a wɔyɛ edwuma no,
Wotsiatsia M'anamɔn mu;
Hɔn a wɔyɛ edwuma a wɔnnkasa n';
Wɔyɛ Nyame N' pɛ krɔnkrɔn;
Onnhia dɛ ebɔhwehwɛ M' bio,
Mowɔ wo nkyɛn beebiara;
Pirew ɔbo n' na ibohu Me,
Paa dua n' mu na mowɔ hɔ.

. Mbrɛ edwuma biara tse no,
Ma ɔkra a ɔyɛ n' fahodzi;
Dɔ na ehumbɔbɔr a wɔkyerɛ
Ma nyimpa n', wɔyɛ ma Me.
Onnhia dɛ ebɔhwehwɛ M' bio;
Mowɔ Wo nkyɛn beebiara;
Pirew ɔbo n' na ibohu me,
Paa dua n' mu na mowɔ hɔ.

. Meserɛ daadaa ahoɔdzen a 
Yebisa a hɛn nsa ka n'; 
Ɔnye adwen a onnhwinhwin
Na ɔka Woara ho daa;
Ɔdan mbrɛ mahyɛ W' enyimnyam
Mepen som biara do.

. Som biara a Wo pɛ kyerɛ me no 
Mennyɛ ho akɔmpew;
Na me kra ehu nokwar n' a
Ɔyɛ Wo mba adehye n';
Na ɔdɔ etuhoakyɛ bra
Yɛ adehyedzi koraa.

. JESUS, Nyame akyɛdzé a minyim,
Mibisa Wo sor akyɛdze n’;
Hue nkwa nsu gu mo do sesei,
Ͻnye Wo Sunsum na Wo su;
Ewuradze, Ͻwo nye nkwa nsunyiwa n'
Afei ma munhu W' m'akoma m’. '

. Hɛn Nua, Agyenkwa, Tsir 
Ɔyɛ hɛn adze nyin;
Hɛn a yɛka No do n'
Yebohu N'enyim ntsɛm,
Ɔno nye hɛn nsɛfo esiarfo n';
Hɔ hɛn akwantu bɔbɔ adze.

. Israel akodɔm Sahen, 
Sor akwantufo hɔn kwangyafo,
Wo nwinwin ase na yɛtse,
Wo dɔ mununkum kata hɛn do;
Hɛn tum, W'adom; hɛn mbra, W'asɛm;
Hɛn ewiei, Ewuradze N'enyimnyam.

. Dɛ Wo Sunsum gya hɛn yi dze, 
Yɛnnkɔfom kwan wɔ sar yi do;
Yennhia dɛ daa wɔkyerɛ hɛn kwan,
Yɛnnkɔfom hɛn Nyame kwan no;
Mbusu nye suro bɔkɔ ekyir,
Ber a ɔdɔ kɛse bɛn hɛn.

. GYEFO, gya hɛn dɛ Guanhwɛfo;
Yehia Wo nhwɛdo pa no;
Nyɛn hɛn wɔ W'edzidzibea do;
Isiesie hɛn ma W'edwuma;
Jesus Siarfo,
Atɔ hɛn, yɛyɛ Wodze.

. Ma yɛnhwehwɛ W'enyimpa ntsɛm,
Ma yɛnyɛ ntsɛm nyɛ Wo pɛ;
Domfo Ewuradze, hɛn Agyenkwa,
Bra na bɛhyɛ hɛn mu ma;
Jesus Siarfo,
Adɔ hɛn, kɔ do dɔ hɛn.

. Agyenkwa, fa hɛn bɔn kyɛ hɛn; 
Hɛn mberɛwyɛ nyina Ɔwo nyim;
'Wo dzii hɛn kan nantseew wiadze,
'Wo tsee no mu yaw wenwen;
Eyɛɛ ankonam, dze berɛ,
Na fona kyiin sar no do.

. O EGYA, gya hɛn wɔ asomdwee akwan mu;
Wo nsa enngya hɛn abamba a, yɛtɔ gon,
'Kyingye tu hɛn bo, 'werɛhow yɛ kɛse;
Gya hɛn Christ mu, nokwar, nkwa na kwan no.

. O Egya, gya hɛn wɔ akwan pa no mu;
Sɛ hɛn nko nam a, yefintsiw enyifura m',
Sɛ yɛnam anafua sum kebii mu a;
Wo nkotsee na yɛnye W' tu hɛn kwan sɔnn.

. Gya m', O gya m', Jehovah tumfo, 
Kwantunyi a menam sar do;
Meyɛ mberɛw, 'wo yɛ hoɔdzenfo;
Fa Wo tum nsa n' suo mo mu;
Sor edziban!
Nyɛn me ndɛ na mber nyina.
 
. Bue nsunyiwa hyɛnhyɛnn n' sesei, 
Mbrɛ yarsa nsu fi pem no;
Ma ogya na mununkum fadum
Ngya m' m'akwantu nyina mu:
Gyefo tumfo!
Yɛ mo mboa na me kyɛm daa.

. Hɛn nda nyina m' kyerɛ hɛn
Kwan a yɛmfa do;
Gya hɛn konyim mu ara
Wɔ atamfo nyina do;
W'abɔfo nwowaw hɛn
Ber a mbusu abɛn;
Fa kyɛ hɛn na gya hɛn
Wɔ da bɔn no mu.

. WONDUOM! Hɛn asɛm nye n';
'Namɔn na ndze mbɔ m',
Hwehwɛ dza ɔwɔ enyim,
Yenntwa hɛn kɔn 'kyir;
Ogya fadum no dzɛw
Dzi nsordaafo kan;
Hɛn Sahen dzi enyim yi,
Woana bɔbɔ hwea?
Hom mfa sar n' do nkɔ enyim,
Wɔ fona nye ɔko m';
Jordan pem wɔ hɛn enyim,
Zion ne kan hyerɛn.

. Ɔsoɛɛr fii wu mu bio maa hɛn;
Ɔfowee kɔr sor ma odzi hen;
Ɔsomaa No Sunsum brɛɛ hɛn
Dɛ ongya hɛn na ɔnhyɛ hɛn dzen.

. JESUS yε Oguanhwεfo pa;
Jesus wui gyee nguan no nkwa;
Ɔyε m’dze, meyε Nedze;
Dza mihia No mu n’ minya,
N-kwà ahomgye edziban, ’
Nyame mu ndzepa biara.

. Meyar a ɔma metsé apɔw,
Ogya me kɔ asomdwee mu;
Okenyan me kré a ɔahaw,
Ɔma tsénenee tsim mo mu;
Ɔno a obowui gyee me n’,
Ɔda ho dɔ m’ - menntsé ase!

. EWURADZE, kyerɛ m' kwan
Ma ɔnda hɔ;
Mibetsie W'asɛm no,
San si do bio;
Munntu anamɔn kor gyedɛ muhu
Kwan kor a Ɔwoara bɛkyerɛ me.

. Ewuradze, abotar m'
M'bɔtwer, etsim;
Menngye W'asɛm ho kyim,
M'enyidar tsim;
Metar Wo ho a mebɛyɛ dɛn ahera,
M'awerɛkyekyer, Agyenkwa, Kwangyafo?

. Monnkɔ mbrɛ Ɔwo gya me daa nyina,
Mennyɛ aso mma Wo ndze a ewasa m' no;
Meka kan afofor bi do, na mo bɔn m',
Kakraabi na mehyɛ m' Nyɛnko ebufuw;
Naaso idzi yaw mpo a, inngya me hɔ,
Mbom eweɔn Wo tsenabea wɔ m'akoma m'.

. Meyɛ hɔho wɔ wiadze ha,
'Hobrɛadze m' mosoɛ ha;
No mu enyigye na fona
Nnkenyan enyidar na suro;
Mber tsiabaa siw n'adzesɛɛ ano,
No mu dɛw twa mu ntsɛm;
O mbom ahomka a meka do n'
Betsim hɔ afebɔɔ.

. HOM a hom yɛ hom Wura Ne pɛ,
Hom akoma nyɛ botoo daa;
Dabiara hom nka hom bɔn,
Hom a hom nantsew tsenenee mu;
Akra pa a hom wɔ adom mu,
Hom nhwehwɛ hom Ewuradze.

. Akra a hom enyi gye mper
Nkɔ sor a ɔyɛ krɔnkrɔn no;
Hom ngye N'anohoba no,
Nye adom a ɔwɔ dze ma;
Hom nka do, mma wɔnngow mu,
Kɛpem dɛ hom hu N'enyim

. Yɛ m' Nyansaa, Ɔwo m'Asɛm nokwafo;
Mowɔ Wo nkyɛn, Ewuradze, 'nye m' wɔ hɔ;
Eyɛ m' Egya kɛse, meyɛ W' ba pa;
Sɛ etse mo mu a, menye Wo yɛ adze kor.

. Tsetseber a etwa m' n', yɛyeew hɛn fie kwan;
Nna yennhu adze;
Hɛn enyi furae, hɛn anamɔn tɔɔ dɔnsuar;
Yeennhu Wo koraa!
Na Ɔwo Ewuradze hun hɛn mbɔbɔr;
Wo nsa kaa hɛn enyi ma obuebuei.

. Sesei Alleluia gyegye hɛn kwan m' 
Enyigye mu;
Wo dɔ eyi hɛn yaw na adzesoa duudur
Kan wɔ hɛn enyim;
Enyimnyam nka Wo, Ɔwo a W' dɔ agye hɛn,
'Nyimnyam nka W' wɔ ndzɛmba akɛse a ayɛ ntsi.

. Jesus, gye mo sunsum,
Motwer Wo bra na su;
Fa 'guan yi kɔ fie na
Ahwehwɛ n' biara;
Kora ɔkra yi do sɔnn
Na Ɔwo atɔ no.

. Nyimpa, per nya enyimnyam n'; 
Ku wo ntsin nya kan no;
Ma enyidar ndzi kan nkosuom'
Kyerɛ ɔyew W'enyi do,
Dzi dɛw, ao, dɛtse na nso,
Nyame bɛyɛ wodze;
Nedze nye w', No nko Nedze
Na 'bɛyɛ afebɔɔ.

. ƆSOR fie! Ɔsor fie!
Adehye-mba hɔn fie;
Adzesaa so nnyi ɔsor fie,
Mbom anapa a ɔmmpa a;
M'enyi akɛda ɔsor fie,
M'akoma dzi yaw wɔ ha;
Wonndzi yaw biara wɔ hɔ,
Merebɛn ho kakra.

. M'Ewuradze wɔ ɔsor fie,
'Nye N'abɔfoe wɔ hɔ;
Na bɔn bi nnyi ɔsor fie
Na nsɔhwɛ so nnyi hɔ;
Ndze bi a ofi sor fie
Rowosow m'asowa mu;
Na sɛ modwen ɔsor fie ho a,
Nyinsu hyɛ m'enyiwa ma.

. Hɔn a modɔ hɔn wɔ sor fie
Refrɛfrɛ me akɔ hɔ;
Ahomgye na asomdwee wɔ sor fie,
Na bra a ɔnnsɛɛ ara da;
Na owu bi nnyi sor fie hɔ,
Awerɛhow so nnyi hɔ;
Christ nye hɛn nkɔ ɔsor fie
Wɔ dɔ a onnyi ewiei mu.  Amen.

. O nkwa a ɔahyɛ hɔn amaama a! 
Sor mframa a wɔgye n' yɛ dɛw;
Enyigye n' bor hɛn adwen do;
Onnyi kabea.

. N-dɛ yɛ ekan da; 
Nyame, ma kan mbra ndɛ;
Hɛn Anapawi, hyerɛn hɛn do,
Na pam hɛn sum nyina.

. N-dɛ yɛ ahomgye da; 
Hyɛ hɛn ahoɔdzen mu;
Hue Wo bɔw nwinwin no ma hɛn,
Dwedwe 'koma a ɔahaw,

. N-dɛ yɛ asomdwee da; 
Fa W'asomdwee ma hɛn;
Ma mansotwe nyina mbɔ adze 
Ma wongyaa n-tokwaa.

. N-dɛ yɛ mpaabɔ da: 
Ma asaase mpinkyɛn sor;
Ma hɛn akoma nhwehwɛ Wo,
Bra behyia hɛn wɔ ha

. ’Nyidzi na ayɛyi nka Jesus,
Ne da krͻnkrͻn yi mu nyina;
Obia’a ntow Jesus N'ayɛyi;
Mma wonngyaa ber kakraabi mpo,
Ma iyi nkͻ do ber nyina;
Hom nka N'ayɛyi na dͻ nko.    Amen.

. Sor 'sɛnkyerɛdze, asaase asomdwee,
Hianyi kyɛfa, na akyenkyendur;
Nyame dase, sor ndzɛmba ho;
Ewia wɔ ayarsa wɔ no mu.

. KAN a ofir kan, bue m'enyi,
Afei adze rekye fofor;
Adom Ewia, pam sum no;
Ma m'Ahomgye da anapa nhyerɛn
W'enyigye nhyira ewia n',
M'ahomgye da yɛ enyika.

. Hɛn dɛw na asomdeee bura,
Gya me kɔ Wo nkwa esu ho;
Ɔwo gye m' kra fi wiadze;
Fa adom na mbɔbɔrhu nyɛn 
Hyira W'asɛm do ma ɔnsow
Aba bafuu nkyerɛ Wo dɔ.

. Dadwen nye egyangyandze nyina
Nyɛ da no krɔnkrɔn mma Nyame;
Bra, Otumfo nyimyamfo,
Na bɛhyɛ asɔrdan yi ma;
Me kra nnkehinhim n-dɛ,
M'bɔhom Wo dɔ mu ara nko.

. Ma hɛn ɔdwe na ahobrɛadze,
Eso yɛnyɛ dza ɔtsen;
Pam isum amma yeemmfintsiw;
Nyimpa nantsew sɔnn kan mu.

. Ma hɛn ɔdwe na ahobrɛadze,
Eso yɛnyɛ dza ɔtsen;
Pam isum amma yeemmfintsiw;
Nyimpa nantsew sɔnn kan mu.

. Wo kan enyim siw mpo a,
Yɛnnkɛgye Wo kyim;
Ennka ho a ɔbra yɛ sum;
Wo mu owu mpo hyerɛn.
Kan mu Kan, hyerɛn hɛn do
Hɛn akwantu mu;
Kɔ do dzi hɛn enyim
Kɛpem da a onnyi ewiei.

. Mo Wura, ma muntu ehu dɛm: 
Gya m' twa bɔn wiadze yi mu;
Fa W'adom no suo mo mu,
Ma minnya kwan wɔ Wo nkyɛn.
M'ewia nye me kyɛm nye 'Wo;
Gya mo mfom 'koma 'i, weɔn no;
Adom nye enyimnyam fir Wo;
O mo Wura, hue gu mo do.   Amen.

. Nyame yɛ wodze; mma nnsuro
'Tamfo a ɔwɔ wo mu;
Nyame bɛba wo honam m',
Ma bɔn aabɔ adze;
Nyame bɛsɛɛ ɔbɔnfo n',
Ama wo konyimdzi m' dɛw; 
Nyame bɛpam n' na ɔaka
Dɛ, Sɛɛ hɔn, sɛɛ hɔn nyina!

. Ma nkorɔfo no nyi W' ayɛw,
Na asaase bɔsow n'aba,
Nyame behyira nyimpa;
Nyimpa dze n' ho ma Nyame;
Ase mba nye ɔsorfo nyina
Bɛtsena dɛw na dɔ kor mu.

. Awerɛhow nsa mia hɛn,
Wiadze haw hiahia hɛn ho;
Ma hɛn kra nnya W'asomdwee;
  Jesus, gye hɛn nkwa.

. HOM mma hom akoma do! Yɛma do ma Wo;
Yennyi obi bio wɔ Wo nan adze;
Hom mma hom akoma do! Yɛbɔ mu ma do,
Yɛma do, yɛma do ma Ewuradze!

. Afei, ekyir yi totorobɛnto hɛn a,
Hom mma hom akoma do! Ɔgyegye hɛn asomu;
Akoma nyina bɔbɔ mu agye do;
Yɛma do, yɛma do ma Ewuradze!

. Wo so yɛ nyimpa, nyim ne nyina,
Ͻbɛkaa me dɛ edͻ me;
Bɛn me, annyɛ a m’bͻhwease;
Mo Wura, nkwa, m’adze nyina.

. Mobͻ mo mu adze komm W’enyim;
Tsie me mpaabͻ a misi do yi; 
O ma m’afͻrbͻ yi ndzi mu,
Mo Wura, nkwa, m’adze nyina.

. Agyenkwa Christ, Nyimpa nye W' so; 
Wɔatseetsee Wo, wɔasɔ W' ahwɛ;
Ema Wo dɔ enyi do a, ihu
Epirakur a fɛr dze rusuma n'.

. AGYENKWA, hyira hɛn ana yɛakɔ;
Fa W'asɛm hyɛ hɛn adwen mu;
Na ma akoma mu nkenyan,
Ahobrɛadze dɔ na pɛ pa.
   Wɔ nkwa adzekyee nye wu sum mu,
   O Jesus brɛfo, yɛ hɛn kan.

. Nyame, fa Wo nhyira gya hɛn kwan, 
Dom hɛn dɛw na asomdwee;
Ma ankorankor yennya Wo dɔ
Mfa ndzi nkwagye adom ho dɛw;
Ao, hyɛ hɛn dzen
Wɔ bra sar akwantu yim'.

. Yɛdze ndaase na ntonton ma W' 
Wɔ Wo nsɛmpa dɛɛdɛw n' ho;
Nkyɛ Wo nkwangye no ho aba
Asow hɛn akoma nye bram';
Nkyɛ Woara so
Yeehu W' hɛn nkyɛn afebɔɔ.    Amen.

. Hue Wo Sunsum gu hɛn akra do;
Fa abrabɔ pa san ma hɛn;
O ma Wo dɔ no nkenyan hɛn,
Na ma yɛnsow aba Wo mu.

. CHRIST hɛn kutuwdo - bo,
No nko do na yɛtow;
N'ahotsewfo nko hyɛ
Sor abanguado ma;
Yɛdze hɛn enyidar na enyigye
Hyɛ No dɔ na adom mu sesei.

. Ͻbra n’akwan horow mu,
Yɛdzé enigye nantsew;
Hɛn a yeduaa mbusu mu n’,
Yetsia N’anamͻn mu,
Ber a ͻwͻ akoma biara mu n’;
Nya Nyame N’ kuropͻn.

. Yɛdze hɔn dɛw brɛ hɔn Wura;
Hɔn ndwom sian ba hɛn so nkyɛn; 
Sunsum a ɔtoow ndwom wɔ hɔn mu n', 
Ɔdze No ndwom so ma hɛn;
Yɛnye hɔn tow ndwom kor ara;
Yɛma do, yɛdze kɔ sorsor,
Ndwom a ɔmmbɔ adze da.

. Ahotsewfo a hom reba nyina,
Hom nkɔ do ntow ndwom dɛɛdɛw;
Mma hom nngyaa ndwom n' tow ara da; 
Hom nkɔ do ntow afebɔɔ;
Hom wɔ ahotɔ wɔ hom tsenabea,
Adom a onnyi ewiei wɔ ha,
Hyira Nyia ɔma mbordo n'.

. Akɔaba fi asaase do;
Yɛyɛ hom etuu fɛkuwbɔ mu;
Ofi akoma mapa mu,
Na hom ngye no Jesus dzin mu.

. W'ABASA dzen ntsi yehyira Wo, hɛn egyanom Nyame;
Ɔwo dze Wo poma na W'abaa abɔ 
W'akwantufo ho ban;
Ɔwo afrɛ hɛn akɔ kwan a ekyingyefo enntu da ho;
W'abasa dzen ntsi yehyira Wo, hɛn egyanom Nyame.

. Yɛyɛ kandzea bi a onndum da ho aweɔmfo mapa;
Yɛyɛ afɔrmbukyia ho ahwɛdofo a ebɛn hɛn;
Yɛyɛ Wo fahodzi mba a yɛdeda famu;
W'abasa dzen ntsi yehyira Wo, hɛn egyanom Nyame.

. Ma W'enyim no sunsuma no ntwa hɛn mpasuar no ho nyia;
Fa akokodur a edze maa ewuakɔr no bɔ hɛn esu;
O fa hɛn dua kwan a W'ahotsewfo duaa mu no mu;
W'abasa dzen ntsi yehyira Wo, hɛn egyanom Nyame.

. Ma yɛnnom nkɔ sunsum kor mu;
Bɔ hɛn esu wɔ Wo dzin m';
Na daa yɛndwen ahobrɛadze m',
Na dua dɛw mu kasa.

. Egya, hwɛ Wo Ba a oruwu n',
Na tsie bɔgya a ɔkasa sor n';
Na ma W'adom nyin mbra hɛn do;
Asomdwee, tsenenee, dɛw na dɔ,
Dza ewɔ nyina, na mbrɛ etsie biara,
W'ahenman mbra akoma biara m'.  Amen.

. Ma ne ndze nyɛ wansa daa; 
Ɔmbɔ nkaa wɔ atsɛmbu ho;
Ɔnka Agyenkwa pa ho nsɛm,
Yɛserɛ Wo, tsie hɛn.

. Tsetsew ne nkyehoma mu; 
Tseam ma ko na 'nyiber ngyaa;
Dom no ɔsor asomdwee n',
Yɛserɛ Wo, tsie hɛn.

. Ma ne nyimdzi nyɛ krɔnkrɔn; 
Ɔnka bɔn no dɔm nyina ngu;
Ɔmboa aman nyina ngu;
Yɛserɛ Wo, tsie hɛn.    Amen.

. Nyame, wiadze akodze sa a, 'botum aboa;
Nyame, bɔn ruku hɛn a, 'botum agye nkwa;
Nyame, Wo botan do, 'wu anaa hɛll nnyi tum;
Dom hɛn W'asomdwee.

. Bér a abofra dzé anofamfa,
Mbaabun a wͻyɛ fɛw; 
Nkͻdaa na mberwa a wͻagow,
Dze mpaabͻ hwehwɛ W’;
Bér a kunefo ’wérɛhonyi
Bͻbͻfo su kyérɛ W’;
Bér a egyanka dze ne nsɛm
Nyina ba W’enyim no:

. Wiadzenyi akoma m’ yarfo
Ma ne kra do sor;
Bér a ’dzesɛɛfo bu n’ kͻn ekyir
Hwɛ n’Egya No dͻ n’;
Bér a ’hokyérɛnyi fi no ntuw m’
Kotow hwehwɛ Wo n’;
Ber a dzebͻnyɛnyi dze n’ bͻn
Ba W’adom eguà enyim n’:    Amen.

. YENNHUN Wo dɛ mbrɛ ɔfata,
Yennsuaa W'adom, nyansa na tum;
Wiadze egyapadze na ber yi m'
Ndzɛmba ahyɛ hɛn adwen ma;
Ewuradze, ma yenhu W' nokwar n;
Yɛ hɛn enyansafo ma yenhu W'.

. Yɛnndɔɔ Wo dɛ mbrɛ ɔfata,
Na ammfa hɛn ho dɛ Ɔwo dɔ hɛn;
Yɛnnhwehwɛɛ bɛn a ebɛn hɛn n' yie,
Hɛn kɔn nndɔ yie dɛ yebohu W';
Ewuradze, ma hɛn akoma a m' tsew
Ma yenhu dɛ Ɔwo nye ɔdɔ n'.

. Brɛ W'aso adze na tsie,
Bue W'enyiwa na hwɛ;
Hɛn dɔ yɛ enyimguase;
Ɔsɛ dɛ yɛba W' nkyɛn,
Yɛyɛ n' dɛ W'adom tse,
Yɛ no dɛ mbrɛ epɛ.

. OWURA, Wodze nye m’; matse Wo ndze,
Na ͻkàa Wo dͻ kyerɛɛ me;
Naaso mo kͻn dͻ dɛ mosoɛr gyedzi m’,
Na wͻbͻtwe me abɛn Wo.
   Twe me bɛn ho, bɛn ho siar Ewuradze;
   Kͻ mbeamuduà à iwui wͻ do n’ ho;
  Twe me bɛn ho, bɛn ho, siàr Ewuradze,
  Kͻ W’epirakur à ͻsom bo n ’ ho.

. ’Homado na ͻpɛ m’
Yeedua yi mu sͻnn;
Yefaa nsu na ogya m’ n’,
Ͻno nà ͻgyee hɛn;
Wiadze nɛ abͻnsam nsamu
Yedzi nyim we N’ mu;
Ͻyɛ hɛn Gyefo pa,
Ͻtse dɛm daapem.

. San W’ekyir, dͻm Ewuradze, san!
Hwɛ W’akowaà a n’abaw egura;
Musu me gyedzi a minnyi ntsi;
Bio, fa kyɛ m’ dɛ minnyi gyedzi;
Mo sunsum nsan mbɛda W’abaw m’,
Na Agyenkwa no ntsi, hyira me.

. Mbͻbͻr a ihu ͻkra a edͻ n’ ntsi,
Sesei pam bͻn a ikyir n’ ma ͻnkͻ;
Ma menyɛ dza Ͻwo egye to m’,
Ͻwo nà egye dza mepɛ to m’;
Ͻwo bɛpɛ dɛ efrɛ m’ Wodze,
Mobͻbͻ mbͻdzén afrɛ W’ medze.

. Afei ͻda W’akoma mu.
Dza hɛn akoma pɛ no yie; 
Gyaa hɛn haw ho nkrumsi n’ sor;
Wo nhyira a wonnsusu no;
Kyerɛw dzin a yɛdze ama W’ sesei n’,
Kyerɛw n’ wͻ heaven buukuu no mu.
		Amen.

. Jesus a wɔasera No n' na hwɛ N'enyim, 
Ehwɛ hɛn a, hwɛ hɛn wɔ Christ no mu;
Mma nnhwɛ hɛn dɛ yeetsiatsia W'adom do;
Mma nnhwɛ hɛn mpaabɔ nye gyedzi nwinwin n':
Na hwɛ! hɛn mfom nye hɔn ho akatua,
Wo Ba, hɛn Wura, N'amandzehu so ntam'.

. Hɔn so a yɛdɔ hɔn kyɛn adze nyina n', 
Yedua Christ do yɛtotɔ serɛ ma hɔn;
O fa W'ehumbɔbɔr fua hɔn Wo bom',
Bɔ mbɔdzen nyina hɔn kra ne yie ho;
Sie hɔn krɔnn fi emumuyɛ nkekaa ho,
Fa dzenhyɛ wie dwuma n' ma wɔnkɔ kan.

. Ɔwo gyina krɔnkrɔnbea ha,
Ber a woekum Wo ama abɔn;
Bɔgya petsee n' kasa, bɔ mpaa,
Na ɔwɔ hɔ ma nyimpa abrɛfo;
Wo bɔgyaa n' da ho ara pon hɛn
Na ɔka nkwagyesɛm wɔ mbea nyina.

. Egya, Woara ennsi dan yi a, 
Wɔnnkɛfa edu beebi;
Gyefo, Woara ennhyira do a,
Hɔn dɛw bɛdan hɔn yaw;
Na hweeara nnkotum asɛɛ
Awar a ehyira do;
Ɔdɔ a Wo Sunsum tsew ho
Yɛ dɔ a ɔmmbɔ adze da.

. Fa W'adom mbordo n oma hɛn,
Ɔnsera hɛn, ɔntsew hɛn enyim;
Pam atamfo, ma asomdwee;
Mbrɛ ewɔ mbusu nntum mmba hɔ.

. Kyerɛ hɛn ma yenhu dɛ Egya n'
Ɔnye Ɔba n' nye Wo yɛ kor;
Ama ber a onnyi ewiei mu
Iyi nko aayɛ hɛn daa ndwom, -
     Ayɛyi nka Wo dzin mbersantsen;
    Egya, Ɔba, nye Sunsum Krɔnkrɔn!  Amen.

. Mo Wura, kasa! Mennsɛ bi mpo a,
Sɛ enntsee me ndze a, mma monnkɔ;
Mo Wura kasa! Na Woara nyim
M'akoma n'akɔndɔdze;
Woara nyim n'ehiadze nyina,
Kasa na hyira m' prɛko.

. Mo Wura, kasa! Na yɛ m' krado,
Sɛ metse Wo ndze ampa a;
Setsie mu na enyigye mu,
Ma mindzi W'asɛm ekyir;
Mo Wura, mayɛ aso ritsie,
O mo Wura, kasa kyerɛ me!

. Hɛn Wura, tsena hɛn mu;
Ma hɛn W'adwen no bi;
Ma yɛmfa hɛn ahom
Nyina ndɔ Wo, nsom Wo;
Na hɛn bra aakyerɛ
Wo mbofra mbrɛ etse,
Na yɛdze hɛn suban
Aatwe Wo mba nyina.    Amen.

. Ma m' W'ahoɔdzen, Nyame Tumfo,
Nkyii ma aahow mbɔ, nsenaman mbobɔ m';
Mbɛyɛ W' dasefo nokwafo;
Mutum ne nyina yɛ Wo dzin m'.

. Bue abow a wiadze nye hɛll
Per dɛn ara a, wonnkotum atow mu;
Ma W'asɛm ngye ntaa wɔ hɛn mu;
Na hɛn adom aba ntsena hɔ.

. Yenyim dɛ dza yɛwɔ suar koraa,
Yenyim hɛn esintɔ dɛ
Yenntum nnyɛn akra a kɔm dze hɔn;
Ewuradze, yɛdze brɛ W';
Yɛdze hɛn ehiadze gu W' nsamu a,
Ɔyɛ ahonya mbordo;
Yɛ ɔdodow ebisadze ma hɛn,
Na fa W' dɔ hyɛ hɔn ma.  Amen.

. Fa Wo dzin ho dɔ no sɔ gya
Wɔ hɛn akoma nyina mu;
Kesi dɛ aman nyinara,
Bɛgye Wo mbeamudua no;
Ma hen enyi ntsim Wo mbeamudua n' do;
Nweɔn nkesi dɛ ebɛba,
Yɛabɔ asen do, asɔ nkandzea hoo;
Ewuradze, fa W' nkowaa kɔ fie.   Amen.

. Yɛbɔbɔ mpaa aboa,
Yɛbɛma bi dze aboa;
Yɛbɛpa hɛnho ekyir;
Kakra a yɛbɛyɛ n'
Bɔboa hɛn Wura No twadwuma yi bi.

. HOM nkotow Hen nyimnyamfo a ɔwɔ sor;
Mfa ndaase nkamfo No tum nye No dɔ;
Hɛn kyɛm nye hɛn Gyefo, Mbersantsen Panyin,
Ahoɔfɛw nye No buw, ayɛyi abɔ N' do.

. Wɔdze Ewuradze atsɛmbu hu No;
Ɔboa bɔbɔfo a ohu amandze:
Onyim n'awerɛhow nyina;
Ɔwerɛhonyi nnkɛka mmɔn daa,
Nyia ɔdze su dua dze dɛw bobu,
Nyia ɔdze yaw hwehwɛ dze dɛw hu.

. MA ndwom no ndu wiadze nyina;
Jesus Christ yԑ Owura;
Tow N'ayԑyi, bɔ dawur,
Ntonton nka Ne dzin.
Ɔman na gyirama biara
Mbɔ m' ntow enyimnyam ndwom no.

. Ma ndwom no ndu wiadze nyina;
Omfi boka pomu,
Beebi a adzekyee hyԑ ase,
Dԑw, kan na ahotɔ m';
China dɔmpepe nsuo m' bi,
Mfa nkodu India mbew do.

. Ma ndwom no ndu wiadze nyina;
Beebi a Kramosom
Agye ntaa wɔ fie nyina m';
Twitwa hɔn mpokyerԑ m'
N'ayԑyi mfi Ebibirim pomu
Mfow nkodu ne mbew nyina do.

. Ma ndwom no ndu wiadze nyina;
Bea a hyewber yԑ dԑw n',
Ma ndwom krɔnkrɔn no mu nsԑm
Ngyegye ekyirekyir;
Kwaa tuntu sunkamm nyina mu 
Na mpoano so ngye ndwom n' do.

. Woegyaa nyԑnko, fie na ebusua,
Ewuradze, Ɔwo na asoma hɔn;
W'anohoba na ogya hɔn,
Ber a wotwa po na asaase;
O ka hɔn ho!
Woara gya hɔn dwudwoodwo.

. Ahenman, asɔrdan, tumdzi;
Ewuradze bԑma nsa aka;
Egya, ma W'ahendzi mbra
Obiara n'akoma mu.   Amen.

. KWAAMU nkokwaa hom ndzi dԑw,
Esutsen, mbepɔw m' nsu,
Hom ntsie ndze a ɔreba n';
Mbɔnsa, asaase ntow ndwom;
Sԑ hom Ewuradze kyԑree a, ɔabԑn;
Ɔdze atsԑmbu na konyim nam.

. Boka nsaase hom nnyan,
Hom mba bԑyԑ adehye;
Hom mfi tsetse nda n' mu,
Nsoԑr nkɔ fahodzi mu;
Onnyiewiei da no enya epue
Wɔ ekyirkyir awɔw nkokwaa n' do.

. Ber a hom rokɔ fie yi,
Hom mu biara ntow ndwom;
Hwԑ yefi Kwaamu, Boka,
Anee, Pomu na yԑaba;
Nyame Kurow, yԑayԑ adehye,
Yԑreba abedzi hen wɔ wo mu.

. NYAME ahotsewfo, hɔn haw etwa m',
Woedzi konyim wɔ ɔbra ko yi m',
Wonnhia kyɛm na nkrantsee biara;
Wobubu mu gu hɔn Wura enyim;
O 'hotsewfo a woehyira hɔn,
Jesu N'anan ase na wɔhom.

. 'Hotsewfo Nyame, yesu frɛ W';
O Agyenkwa, dzi ma hɛn sor;
Sunsum Krɔnkrɔn, Gyafo, Nyɛnko,
Fa W'adom boa hɛn kesi ewiei;
O 'hotsewfo a woehyira hɔn,
Atsena paradise ahomgye m'.  Amen.

. Mbusu n' mpo nhyira wɔ mu
Dɛ yaw nda n' so;
Nyimpa afɔbu wɔ ase;
Sor Egya n' ayɛyi a.

. Fa Wo nkwagye kɛse no bɛn,
Eguambaa a bɔn ntsi iwui;
Hyehyɛ hɔn a afrɛ hɔn n' nyina ma
Na fa Wo tum dzi hen,
Aman nyina Ahwehwɛdze, bra,
Wo ndɔmmumfo afe fie;
W'anohoba ahyɛnsew n' mpue wimu;
Ɔhen Ba Agyenkwa, bra. Amen.

. TSIE! Mfeduonum 'fahyɛ ndwom;
Ne dede tse dɛ aprandaa;
Anaa po a ɔapram kɛse
Bu asorɛkye bogu mpoano,
Hallelujah! Ewuradze
Nyame Tumfo bedzi hen;
Hallelujah! Ma asɛm no
Ntahye wiadze nyinara.

. Ɔdze tum a onnyi mbanano,
Bedzi hen wɔ mbea nyina;
Sɛ ɔsor bobɔw kɔ mpo a
Ɔbɔkɔ do eedzi hen;
Ewiei n', dasanyi n' tamfo n'
Bɔhwe ase wɔ N' poma ase;
Hallelujah! Nyame m' Christ,
Christ m' Nyame, yɛ adze kor.

. Ɔdze N'asɛm bɔɔ adze nyina;
Ɔhyɛɛ dɛ ɔmbra na ɔbae;
Asaase, ɔsor na po nyina,
Ka bɔ mu yɛ wiadze kor;
Ndzɛmba a wohu bosoom hyerɛn, 
Na dza wɔhom wi yi ase,
Afebɔɔ na afebɔɔ.

. Oyi na tsetse adzehufo
Bɔɔ anosɛɛ toow No ho ndwom;
Nyia nkɔnhyɛfo no dze hɔn ndze
Kaa No ho asɛm nokwar mu;
Afei Nyia enyi daa N'kwan n' hyerɛn;
Ma abɔdze nyi Ewuradze ayɛw,
Afebɔɔ na afebɔɔ.

. Ɔsorsor, hom ntonton No;
Abɔfo dɔm nyi N'ayɛw;
Etumfo nyina nkotow No,
Hom nkrɔn hɛn Nyame Hen no;
Mma tɛkyerɛma biara nnyɛ komm,
Ma ndze nyinara ntow ndwom,
Afebɔɔ na afebɔɔ.   Amen.

. Wofi ahohia mu aba,
Wɔahor hɔn ntar bɔgya n' mu,
Jesus bɔgyaa n' atsew hɔn ho;
Wɔsɔɔ hɔn hwɛe, wogyinaa dzen;
Wɔsereew hɔn guu fiadze,
Siiw hon abo, paa hɔn seradaa;
Wɔnam Christ No tum do woedzi
Owu na Satan do nyim.

. Mepɛ dɛ meyɛ dɛ Ɔwo;
Ma m' Wo mbrɛhoadze akoma,
'Wo yɛ dɔ, yɛ mbɔbɔrhu;
Ma minnya Wo dɔ adwen no.

. Ɔwo tsenaa ase maa Nyame;
Annhwehwɛ Wo nko W'dze da;
Wo nko W' yieyɛ ennhia Wo da;
Nyame nko nye W'ahomka.

. JESUS Guanhwɛfo pa, tsie me;
Hyira W'eguambaa anafua yi;
Anago sum yi mu bɛn me;
Kora me sɔnn ma adze nkye.

. Ma bɔn nyina fa kyɛ m' koraa;
Hyira 'nyɛnkofo a modɔ hɔn;
Sɛ muwu a, fa me kɔ heaven,
Menye W'bɛtsena hɔ enyigye m'.  Amen.

. Ma m' akokodur mbusu m',
Munhu dɛ Ɔwo tum gye nkwa;
Kora me sɔkyee wɔ Wo nkyɛn;
Ma mentsena Wo dɔ mu.

. Mbofra hɛn fasusu nye No, 
Onyinii dɛ hɛnara,
Kakrabaa, m-berɛmberɛw;
Osui, serewee dɛ hɛnara;
Ntsi hɛn yaw ɔtse ma hɛn,
Na hɛn dɛw onyam' kyɛpɛn.

. Innkegyaa hɛn wɔ huntuma m';
Ebɔɔ nyimpa, ɔnntse W' ase; 
Ɔdwen dɛ wɔammbɔ n' dɛ ombowu;
Naaso ebɔɔ n', Ɔwo etsen.

. Ɔwo yɛ nyimpa na Nyame,
Eyɛ nyimpa krɔnkrɔn, ekrɔn; 
Yɛdze hɛn pɛ, yɛnntse ase;
Yɛdze hɛn pɛ nyina ma Wo.

. Hɛn nhyehyɛɛ nyina wɔ hɔn mber;
Wodzi hɔn mber na wotwa m' kɔ; 
Wɔyɛ Wo kan ho gyansenama,
Na Ɔwo, Ewuradze so sen hɔn.

. Ɔnnkɛkyɛr na aman nyina
Do abosonsɔrfo eetsie
Na woeedzi W'asɛm no do
Aatow hɔn abosom egu;
O fi sor hyerɛn wɔ hɔn do;
Yi Woho kyerɛ dɛ ɔdɔ Nyame;
Agyenkwa pa, kyerɛ hɔn ma wɔmbra 
W'nkyɛn.

. Na mowɔ ɔbra ntsetsee ase;
Ma menyɛ no W'adom mu;
Moroboa m' ho ama ɔbra akodzi;
Ma menyɛ no Wo tum mu.

. Ɔwo ama m' adwen na ɔkra;
Medze bɛyɛ edwuma ama Wo:
Ɔwo wui ma maatsena ase;
M'ahom nyina medze ma Wo.

. Edwumayɛ, dɛw na awerɛhow etwa m';
Hwɛ, ewiei no, yɛtwe bɛn Wo, sɔr Wo,
Sesei a hɛn ndaamba abrabɔ nnyaa mmbaa yi;
Mbofrasɛm etwa m', na mpanyinyɛ wɔ kan.

. Ewuradze, fa Wo nhyira dom hɛn, 
Yebehyia mu bio wɔ ha;
Ma yentu anamɔn nkɔ kan
Wɔ Wo dɔ, gyedzi na surom';
Bɔ hɛn ho ban
Dɛ ebɛn hɛn daa nyina.

. Nyame fa Wo nhyira gya hɛn kwan,
Yɛda ase na ehumbɔbɔr;
Fa nnuhofo nyina mfom kyɛ hɔn;
Wonnya mber mfa ntsen dza asɛɛ n'
Na mma Wo mba
Mmfom Wo Sunsum ara bio.

. Mo nkwa nda a aka n',
Medze beyi N' ayɛw;
Ɔno na owui gyee wiadze nyina;
Mbrɛ me nda tse biara,
Odzi wɔ m' Pomfo no,
Na meetu ne nyina esi hɔn ama No.

. Aman nyina Ewuradze;
Hɛn man hyɛ Wo nsamu;
Ma onsuma Wo mu, ntwer Wo,
Dɛ ne daapem Nyɛnko.  Amen.

. Abɔbɔfo n' da ho rohwɛ
Ahotɔ dɔnhwer no kwan;
Na nkuropɔn m' begyabegya
No retsea mu dɛ bɔn ngyaa;
Na efiefi nye ndɔtɔ ase
Totɔ serɛ asomdwee.

. Hwehwɛ akoma m' ma hɛn nokwar,
Yɛmfa obiara ne kyɛfa mma n';
Yemfi enyigyedze akɔndɔbɔn m',
Yemfi bɔn a ɔma akoma yɛ mberɛw m';
Twe hɛn, na fa Wo poma no
Kyerɛ hɛn na yenhu hɛn mfom.

. Hɛn kasaa na ndzeyɛɛ no bɔn,
Mpirenyim ho apɛbiakyerɛ;
Enyitsew bɔn a wɔfa do
Daa dze bu ekotobɔfo;
Na hɛn bra a no botae nn-hyerɛn,
Hɛn Wura, yɛserɛ, fa n' nyina kyɛ hɛn.

. Ma gya dzendzen a ɔpo kra n'
Ntsew hɛn bɔbew mu sunsum ho:
Hyew bɔn na tu enyimguase ase;
O Nyame! Ka hɔn ho ogya n' mu;
Ma yempue dɛ nyimpa fofor,
'Hotsewfo, nokwar, nyimdzefo.  Amen.

. Mbofra a wonnyi dɛw bi dzi n',
Kyerɛ dɔ fa ma hɔn;
Woeyiyi hɔn ndzinoa ntsi
Fɛw bi nnyi hɔ ma hɔn;
Wo hɔn fofor kɔ ndaamba
Enyidar n' ho.

. Ma nkrumsifo nyina dɛw,
Na awerɛhofo ntow ndwom;
Ma kan nhyerɛn nsaaba biara a
Sum na wu ahyɛ hɔ mā n';
Ma W'ahendzi no nsian mbra
Bɔn mpasuar do.

. Mma ɔnnkyɛr na ma hɛn nkurow
Nhyɛ W'enyimnyam ntar no;
Ma edwumabea nyɛ asɔrfi,
Fie biara mpaabɔ fie;
Kurow biara nya ahoɔfɛw;
Nyame wɔ hɔ!

. Yefi Wo mu, Wo dɔ n' mu mba nye hɛn,
Na Wo dɔ Ba kortoo no No nuanom;
O Sunsum Krɔnkrɔn, sian dɛ ebubur
Bra hɛn akoma mu, ama yaayɛ kor,
Dɛ mbrɛ yɛnye Wo a yɛhwɛ W' no yɛ no;
Na yɛnye hɛn Nua, hɛn Nyɛnko yɛ no.

. Ewuradze, fa W'sor akodze hyɛ hɛn,
Nye kyɛm na Sunsum dɔ nkrantsee no so;
Ma W'asɛm no nnunu hɛn 'ber nyina;
Yɛnnserɛ konyimdzi biara a ommfir Wo,
Ma hɛn, fa kam hɛn; ma dɛw anaa yaw;
Dza ohia nye yebohu dɛ yɛsom Wo.

. Hɛn Awobea, yɛdze wo tuw;
Wo yieyɛ ntsi na hɛn egyaam wui;
Yɛdze hɛn tsir, akoma, nsa,
Sua ma wo mbersantsen nyina.

. Meserɛ Wo, ma minnya Wo;
Ɔwo nye enyigye nyina;
Mibenya enyigye mapa,
Wɔ asaase ha na sor. Amen.

. Na ɔman kor bi so wɔ hɔ a matse nka dada,
Ɔsom bo kɛse ma n'adɔfo, na afei ɔso;
Yɛnnkɛkan n'akofo, na yennkohu ne Hen da;
N'akoban nye nokwar akoma, ne dɛw nye ɔhaw;
Na nkakrankakra, wɔ kommyɛ mu, ne mamfoe dɔr,
No suban nye botooyɛ, n'akwan yɛ asomdwee.

. Tsenenee Nyame! Yeehur Wo bo kɛse,
Naaso W'asɛm tsim hɔ kesi daapem;
Ator na mfom nnkotum atsena Wo nkyɛn;
Ewuradze, ma hɛn asomdwee hɛn ber m'.

. Nkorɔfo nyina nhua Jesus dzin; 
Abɔfo nhwe No fam';
Wɔmfa ahenkyɛw no mbra mbɔsoa N',
Na wɔnhyɛ N' abɔso Hen.

. Bi a wiadze yɛ fɛw, na nyimpa tse dɛw m';
Mber nyina hɔn aman nyin ma ɔsɛɛ;
Wɔkyekyeer aman fi osu adaaso mu;
O nkyɛ nyimpa eenyan efi ne nda m'!
Ma asaase eedzi mu, nyimpa eehu nyansa.

. Wiadze bɛyɛ yie, na nyimpa ayɛ kor;
Gyedɛ 'yi ba na Nyame N' pɛ n' wɔayɛ;
Sesei mpo nyimpa nnsuro dɛ ɔtsea mu
Wɔ dɛw mu fi asaase kɔ sor dɛ;
Asaase ndzi mu, adasa nyɛ kor.

. Sɛ mbusu bɛn hɔn a
Yi hɔn fi ne nyina m';
Na kyerɛ hɔn dɛ Wo
Tum no nnkɛpa ara da;
Yennkotum akɔ mbrɛ wɔwɔ,
Naaso yɛdze hɔn hyɛ Wo nsa.

. Yɛtow hɛn ndzesoa gu Wo do,
Ɔwo Nyame dɔ a emmpa ara da;
Nkwa mu o, 'wu mu o, sɛ yehu dɛ;
Ɔwo bɛn hɛn a, yennsuro yaw.

. Dem ntsi bra bɛsera me kra; 
Pa bɔn nye awerɛhow sum no;
Nyame kan, hyɛ mo mu ma;
Pa m' ekyingye nyinara;
Da Woho edzi mbordo ara
Kodu da a onnyi ewiei n' mu.

. ANAPA dze enyigye kan ba,
Anago sum eguan kɔ;
Kan ne farbaa, 'ma Wo mpuei no
Mpam sum nyina mfi hɛn adwen mu.
Ɔwo ehyira hɛn wɔ hɛn nda m';
Da yi m' kyerɛ hɛn kwan, kora hɛn.

. Boa hɛn ma yenyi W' ayɛw daa,
Na yɛnko ntsia bɔn nyina;
Yennya hɛn mboa nyina mfi Jesu m',
Ɔno a odzii konyim maa hɛn;
Wɔsɔɔ No hwɛɛ wɔ ase ha,
Na onyim hɛn mberɛwyɛ nyina.

. Nyimpa yɛ edwuma du ewimbir a,
Ahomgye a yehia san ba;
Dom hɛn ma yɛngye W'adom no,
Yennya nhyira wɔ dza yɛyɛ m';
Na bea biara a yɛwɔ no,
Yɛnsɔ W'enyi wɔ enyigye m'.  Amen.

. ME kra, bra, soɛr fi wo nda mu;
Adzekyee no
Dze da fofor so reba;
Bra Nyia ɔyɛɛ adze fɛɛfɛw n' nkyɛn,
Hwɛ, fa W'ahom
Kakraba n' nyina tua kaw.

. Fa dɛw hyia ewia a ɔreba n';
Ma w' ahoɔdzen
Nduhuam nyɛ krado ntu hua;
'Nafua sum no etwa mu kɔ,
Edaa hatsee n',
Nyankopɔn hwɛɛ wo do sɔnn.

. Sɔr ma ɔmma dzi mu daa wɔ
Akwan nyina mu;
Ɔmma wo mbɔdzen ndzi mu;
Mbom sɛ epɛ aka bɔn do a,
Ɔnsɛɛ w'akwan,
Nsakyer wo mfa w' nyɛ Nedze.

. Jesus nye dzin a ɔsom hɛn bo,
Dzin a yenntum nnkyerɛ ase; 
Enyigye dzin, enyika dzin,
Aso na akoma dzi dɛw;
Dzin dɛɛdɛw a ɔbor nsusui,
Ɔgye hɛn fi bɔn na hɛll.

. Ɔyɛ Dzin a sɛ wɔbɔ a,
Ɔyɛ dɛw ndwom wɔ asomu;
Nyia ɔdze Dzin yi kotow serɛ 
Nya awerɛkyekye dɛɛdɛw;
Nyia odu ne nyansaa mapa ho n'
Nya sor enyigye n' wɔ ha.

. Jesus nye Dzin a wɔakrɔn no 
Wɔ edzin nyinara mu;
Sɛ obi ka hɛn a, Dzin yi mu
Yegu tamfo n'enyim ase;
Ɔhyɛ hɔn a wonntum nnantsew,
Efurafo, na mpakye dzen.

. Mber a asɛɛ n' kwa hyɛ ananm'; 
Bɔ bra dɛ ndɛ owu nam kwanm';
Kɔ kan kora akyɛdze a Nyame ama n';
Siesie woho ma atsɛmbu da n'.

. Fa nokwar ka w' asɛm biara; 
Mma wo tsibowa mmbu w' atsɛn da;
Nyame enyi hu mbea nyina do
Hyɛ nsumaam' adwen nye nyɛe nsew;

. Ayɛyi nka Nyame dɔyɛfo; 
Asaasemba, hom nkamfo No;
Sor abɔfo hom so ntonton N',
Egya, Ɔba, Sunsum Krɔnkrɔn!    Amen.

. Anapa-wi epue kɔɔ dɛ nhyiren;
Ma hɛn Anapa-wi mapa n' mbra;
Asɛm no a ɔnye Egya n' yɛ kor n',
Egya n' dzi mu wɔ Ba no mu.

. O CHRIST, yɛdze W'akyɛdze
Da fofor yi hyɛ Wo nsa;
Dza ɔdze nam no yennyim
Ntsi yehia Wo mboa mbordo;
Agyenkwa, fa W' mbeamudua n'
Hwɛ do, mma ɔannyɛ ɔsɛɛ ber.

. Sɛ ɔyɔ bɔkɔɔ fɛɛfɛw a,
Woara yɛ hɛn dɛw farbaa;
Sɛ ɔdze haw bi nam so a
Dza ihyira do n' nyina yɛ yie;
Dza yɛserɛ nye dɛ ofi
N'ahyɛse n' mma yɛnnyɛ bɔn.

. Wi asen, adzesaa abɛn;
Agyenkwa, 'nye hɛn ntsena anafua 'i;
'Nye hɛn nkasa, fa W' nsa ka hɛn,
Gya hɛn kɔ asomdwee na kan mu;
W'enyim a wusoɛr adom wɔ mu n'
Mfa ne hyerɛn no mpam hɛn sum.

. N-kwa da ketseaba yi rotwe kɔ; 
Wiadze dɛw repa; n' enyimnyam resen;
N-sakyer na ɔsɛɛ nko ara na muhu;
Ao, 'Wo a ennsakyer da, enye me ntsena.

. Murumua m' enyi a, yi Wo mbeamudua n' kyerɛ m'; 
Hyerɛn wɔ sum mu, kyerɛ m' ɔsor do kwan;
Ɔsor rehyerɛn, wiadze kusuww repa;
N-kwam' o, owum' o, enye me ntsena!

. NDƐ da yi enya etwa m' kɔ;
Hɛn Wura, yɛda W' ase;
Yɛsɔr dɛ mma yɛnnyɛ bɔn
Biara dɛm sumber yi.
O Jesu, ma yengyina W'enyim,
Na adzesaa yi mu kora hɛn.

. Sunsum Krɔnkrɔn, pen na bra
Bɛtsew hɛn ho anafua yi;
Bɛyɛ hɛn akoma Wo fie;
Dan hɛn sum ma ɔnyɛ kan.

. Mbɔbɔrhu ntsi sɛ ebɛma
M'enyigye atweɔn;
Sɛ 'kan nserɛmɛn bi bɛhyerɛn
'Bra do asomdwee mu a;
M'enyigye akoma ntow W' ndwom 
Akwan nyina mu;
Na dza ndaamba dze nam nyina,
Nhyɛ W' dzin enyimnyam.

. Egya, ehu hɛn mbɔbɔr pɛn;
Na 'da ho hwɛ hɛn;
Mbrɛ yɛtse, dza yɛwɔ biara,
Yedua Christ do dze ma W'.

. Mo Guanhwɛfo Ne ndze
Na mepɛ dɛ metse;
N'enyi bɔ mo ho aprɔw,
Kora me No nguankuw mu;
Ɔnyɛn No nguan, 'bɔ hɔn edzin, 
Tur No nguambaa wɔ N'abaw mu.

. Jesus Sɔfopanyin
Dze N' bɔgyaa bɔgyaa bɔɔ afɔr; 
Me tsibowa fɔdzifo
Nnhwehwɛ afɔrbɔ bio;
No bɔgyaa no pataa prɛko, 
Na ɔserɛ ahengua n' enyim.

. Ewuradze Nyame bɛba
Dze No ndɔbaa akɔ fie;
Ɔbɛhyew bɔn nyinara
Wɔ Ne haban m' dɛm da no;
Ɔbɛhyɛ N'abɔfoe ma
Wɔahyew nworahaban no nyina;
Na aba pa no nyina dze
Wɔdze bɛhyɛ san do daa.

. FAMU ha asaase ayɛ ma,
Sor so ahyerɛn;
Obiara reserew
Wɔ 'dɔ kan no mu;
Nyimpa nyina dzi dɛw,
'Yɛyi ahyɛ adwen ma;
Dɛw akoma nye ndze
Ma da biara dɛw.

. Ɔwo nye Guanhwɛfo n',
Merenndan mmfi Wo ho;
Mo Hwɛfo na me Gyafo,
Kɔ do ara hwɛ mo do;
Gya me bɔkɔɔ wɔ Wo nkyɛn,
Tur m' enyigye m' wɔ Wo bo m'.

. Ɔwo nye m' daa Paanoo;
O Christ, Ɔwo nye m' Tsir;
Ma m' ahoɔdzen na ndzepa,
Emi a meyɛ W'akowaa yi;
Enyɛɛn m', maa me edziban,
Ndzɛmba nyina nyin wɔ Wo mu.

. Nkɔnhyɛnyi, yi W'Egya
Ne pɛ pa kyerɛ me;
Ɔdasanyi bi nnkasaa
Dɛ Ɔwo a ifi sor yi;
Wɔdze ndze dzendzen tseatea m',
Kumabaa nyina yɛ Wodze.

. Woenya asaase do fona m' 'homgye,
Wɔdze hɔn esuma Wo mu;
Hɔn adwendwen, ndwuma, tum, yɛ Wodze,
Wɔyɛ Wodze, hɛn so hɛndze a;
Yenyim dɛ bea a wɔwɔ biara
Hɛn ewufo no tse ase ma Wo.

. Hɔ na hɛn nyinsuwa bɔ adze; 
Hɔ na wɔkyerɛ hɛn ase;
Hɔ na ɔsɛndzifo pa n'
Hwɛ hɛn bra nyinara mu:

. Wo dzin kɛse no yɛ nkwagye, 
Ɔma me kra sor enyigye;
Ɔma minya awerɛkyekyer,
Asomdwee, dɛw na onnyiewiei dɔ;
Wo dzin a ɔsom bo no ma me
Fakyɛ na krɔnkrɔn na sor.

. Jesus, eyɛ m'adze nyina;
Me berɛ ne yaw mu ahomgye,
M'akoma a ebubu n'edur,
Ɔko mu na minya asomdwee,
Wɔhyɛ mo do a, ema meserew;
M'enyiwu enyimnyam nye Wo.

. Mber na ntseasee mu bɔw tu kɔ;
Adɔfo a woetwa m' ba;
Na adom kor a etwa hɛn ho ehyia
Kura hɔn nyina m' afebɔɔ.

. CHRIST nye ofi yi a
Yesi yi fapem;
N'afasu nyɛ nkwagye
N'apon ayɛyi;
Na ma n'apongua yi
Nsom bo mma Ewuradze;
Ma akoma a wɔsom ha
No mu nyɛ krɔnkrɔn.

. Ewuradze, Wo Sunsum
Nsɔw anohoba ano;
'Yarfo mbɔ esu wɔ ha,
Wonhu hɔn a wɔayew;
Ha na akoma a abobɔ
Nnya Wo bɔnfakyɛ;
'Nyɛnkofo a wɔatsetsew m'
Nka mbɔ m' bio wɔ ɔdɔ m'.

. Nyimpa nntse ase mma no nko ho,
Ɔwɔ dɛw wɔ nkorɔfo yie ho;
Fɛkuwbɔ m' na yehu ɔbra pa.
Hɛn bra yi mu anyɛnkofo
Hyia dan yi mu ha yɛbɔ mpaa;
Hyira hɛn fɛkuwbɔ do ndɛ.

. KA hɛn nkyɛn ndɛ, adom Ewuradze;
Yetu ofi yi si hɔ ma Wo;
Tsie Wo nkowaa ber a yɛrosɔr yi,
Na ma W'asowa mbra hɛn do.

. Ma wonhu asomdwee krɔnkrɔn,
Dɔ na nokwar wɔ ha daa daa;
Ma akoma berɛfo ahomgye;
Na esiarfo n' soa hɔn ahenkyɛw.

. Bra fie, bra fie!
Na w'akoma apa;
ꓛkwan mu ayɛ sum,
Ayɛ kɔnn, ayɛ hu;
ꓛba dzesɛɛfo!
Bra fie, ao, bra fie!

. Oduyɛfo kɛse n' abɛn
ꓛnye tsimbɔbɔr Jesus;
ꓛkasa mà akoma tɔ yam';
Dɔfo, tsie Jesus Ne ndze!

. Jesus, matɔ mo bo ase morotweɔn,
Bra, bɔbɔ akoma fofor to mo mu;
Hɔn a wɔhwehwɛ W', 'nnse obi Oho da;
Guar m' sesei ma monhoa dέ esukwankyɛba.
